products.name: B5 M:4 Multitasker Multi-Tool Black
products.description:
The M:4 is precision machined from solid bar stock using wire-EDM/CNC and fits discreetly with no visible footprint inside our specially inletted buttpad. Easily accessible without tools simply by pressing the release tabs on the buttpad (sold separately). Dot coded to indicate functions.

The M:4 is a patent pending 1-piece multi-tool for the M4 carbine designed and manufactured by MultiTasker in conjunction with B5 Systems.

Features:

  • Features a slotted screwdriver castle nut spanner 1/2" hex for scope mounts and bolt override
  • Precision machined from barstock
  • Nests inside the b5 systems buttpad
  • MADE IN THE USA

products.name: Area 419 Billet Loading Block .223 Clear Anodized
products.description:
Area 419 Billet Anodized Loading block. The same awesome loading block you’ve come to love from us just anodized to hold up to all your abuse better.

50 places of 308 Magnum or Lapua bolt faced rounds.  Features rubber pads on the bottom to keep from sliding around.

Block is machined in house from 6061-T6 Aluminum.  Dimensions are 9.5″ x 4″ x 5/8″.  Holes are 0.500″ deep and are a tight fit around the case to prevent tipping over.  Hole bottoms have a small “divot” in the very center to catch powder kernels and prevent any possible accidents with primers.

HOLE DIAMETERS

  • 223 – (0.390″)

products.name: Area 419 Fixed Scope Level for Area 419 Rings and Mounts
products.description:
A scope level doesn’t need to be complicated it needs to be visible and needs to be repeatable. This accomplishes these things with a high visibility spirit vial and a simple but versatile design that allows you to mount it to any of several mounting points on Area 419 rings and mounts all based on your preference.

Machined from 6061 Aluminum this product is Made in America and built to last.

products.name: Area 419 SendiT Level Adapter for Area 419 Rings and Mounts
products.description:
Mounting adapter for the popular Send iT electronic level. Allows you to mount vertically (up or down) in any of the multiple mounting locations on our rings and mounts.

Please be sure your Send iT level is new enough that is has the removable thumb screw mount if it is not removable this will not work and you will just want a standard Pic Rail.

Machined from 6061 Aluminum this product is Made in America and built to last.

products.name: Allen Flagging Tape .787"x150' PDQ Orange - Single Roll
products.description: Whether you are plotting a leisurely hike through your property or planning a hunting route the Allen Company Flagging Tape is right for you. Knowing how to mark a trail and what to use is important. Allens flagging tape is an ideal flagging tool to mark property lines hiking trails or when scouting out a campsite. Ergonomically designed to easily be tied to objects or trees while withstanding weather elements with its highly durable construction. Made of vibrant orange-colored material your markings will remain highly visible in the outdoors from long distances apart. Pack includes 3 rolls each measuring 150-feet long providing plenty of material to make your mark along the trail.

products.name: Allen Flagging Tape .787"x150' PDQ Purple
products.description: Mark your territory with the Allen Company No Trespassing Flagging Tape. Whether you are plotting your property lines or planning a hunting route knowing how to mark a trail and what to use is important. The No Trespassing Flagging Tape by Allen serves as a dedicated marker to easily mark designated areas or trees. Made of a vibrant purple-colored material this tape is impossible to miss while out on the hunt. With the ergonomic design this flagging tape can be easily tied to objects or trees while withstanding weather elements with its highly durable construction. Pack includes 12 rolls each roll measures 150-feet in overall length to provide however much you need to mark your way along the trail.

products.name: Allen Trail Marking Tacks
products.description:
These Allen Trail Marking Tacks are highly reflective so you can easily see them from distances up to 200 yards. Use these reflective tacks to mark any type of trail a blood trail during hunting so you can retrace your steps during hiking or any other application you can think of.

Because these Allen Trail Marking Tacks are so reflective they are great for both day and night use. Best of all they come in a convenient 50-pack so you always have as many as you need. If you are looking for a set of highly visible and easy-to-use trail marking tacks look no further than these Allen Trail Marking Tacks.

products.name: Breakthrough Clean Technologies Modern Sporting Rifle Armorers Wrench AR-15
products.description:
The Breakthrough Clean Technologies® Armorer’s Wrench is the ultimate tool for your AR15/M4. Constructed out of durable titanium-plated stainless steel and includes a standard size muzzle device wrench. Easily installs and removes receiver extensions and castle nuts functioning with both Mil-Spec and Pin-Style Barrel Nuts. Compatible with ½” Socket / Torque wrench and comes with a bonus Butt Stock Screwdriver.

Product Features:

  • UNIVERSAL WRENCH: The Breakthrough Clean Technologies universal wrench is the ultimate tool for every day use. Constructed of durable Titanium plated stainless steel.
  • EASY TO ADJUST: Includes standard size muzzle device wrench. Easily install & remove parts. Functions with both Mil-Spec & Pin-Style assembly. Compatible with Socket / Torque wrench.

products.name: Breakthrough Clean Technologies AR15 Carbon Scraper
products.description:
The Breakthrough Clean Technologies AR15 Carbon Scraper is a must-have tool for any AR15 owner. Designed to effortlessly remove carbon build-up from the hard-to-reach areas of your AR15 Bolt Carrier Group this scraper ensures your rifle remains in peak condition. The double-ended blade concealed by protective dual caps and the ergonomic handle make carbon removal quick and efficient. This compact and portable tool is compatible with .223 Cal/5.56mm modern sporting rifles making it an essential addition to your firearm maintenance kit.

Product Features:

  • EFFECTIVE CARBON REMOVAL: Effortlessly scrapes off stubborn carbon build-up from hard-to-reach areas of your AR15 Bolt Carrier Group.
  • ERGONOMIC HANDLE: Provides enhanced leverage and comfort making it easier to tackle tough carbon deposits.
  • PROTECTIVE DUAL CAPS: Keeps the scraper and user safe preventing accidental damage or injury.
  • COMPACT AND PORTABLE: Conveniently sized for easy storage and transport perfect for both field and home use.
  • COMPATIBLE WITH .223 CAL/5.56MM RIFLES: Specifically designed for use with AR15 modern sporting rifles.

products.name: Birchwood Casey Brass Cartridge Case Cleaner
products.description: Super concentrate. This one bottle makes over two gallons of reusable cleaning solution and will clean 8000 medium sized cases. Easily removes resizing lubricant oils grime and stains from brass cartridge cases. Restores them to original finish for reliable operation. Helps remove powder residue. Brass Cartridge Case Cleaner is a safe non-fuming non-etching solution that won't weaken cases. Reusable store solution in a plastic or glass container (not metal) and use when needed.*** Note: THIS PRODUCT CAN NOT BE SHIPPED INTO THE STATE OF CALIFORNIA DUE TO CARB (California Air Resource Board) RESTRICTIONS!***

products.name: Cold Steel Click-N-Cut Exchangeable Blade Knife Black BDS - 2-1/2" Blade Satin
products.description:
The Cold Steel Click-N-Cut (patent pending) features elements that are based on our extremely strong Tri-Ad lock so it?s built for strenuous cutting chores. It comes complete with three interchangeable blades. There is a drop point blade and serrated and plain edged versions of our utility blade. The blades are double the thickness of most blades on the market so they can stand up to the most strenuous cutting scoring scraping and gouging tasks you can imagine. Exchanging a blade is easy. The handle has a lock bar release similar to the release on a folding knife. When the lock bar is pressed the blade slides easily out. Keep the lock bar pressed and slide a new blade in and release the lock bar and the blade will ?click? into place. The Click-N-Cut includes a belt sheath that will hold the knife with one of the blades installed and it has integral pockets for the two remaining extra blades. Extra replacement blades are also available for purchase separately.

products.name: Cold Steel Recon 1 Magnacut Folding Knife 4" Clip Point Blade Black
products.description:
With the Recon M1 Cold Steel is exploring an entirely new addition to their existing lineups just as the folder’s name implies. And that something new—new to us at least—is something for knife enthusiasts to get excited about: the use of world-renowned MagnaCut steel blades in Cold Steel products starting with the all-new Recon M1. Hand-crafted in Italy the Recon M1 boasts unparalleled sharpness resilience and durability courtesy of its MagnaCut steel construction. Known for its toughness as well as extreme wear and corrosion resistance the 4-inch clip-point MagnaCut blade boasts superb edge retention that ensures its ability to effortlessly tackle any challenge—from heavy-duty cutting to intricate piercing tasks. And thanks to its fine microstructure the blade is also far simpler to sharpen than other steels with resistance to wear making it one of the best all-around everyday carry companions on the market today. Outfit that unique feature with a black stonewashed finish then attach it to a no-slip G10 handle and you’ve got the ultimate in steadfast reliability. And thanks to our patented Tri-Ad® locking mechanism safe reliable use comes standard with each tool—guaranteed. The finishing touch? An integrated clip-up pocket clip ensures carry is both convenient and discreet which at just 5.2 ounces is no tough feat for the Recon M1 to master.

  • With a MagnaCut blade this folding knife is the first of its kind from Cold Steel
  • MagnaCut steel resists wear and corrosion and delivers durability that’s second to none
  • Rugged 4-inch 3.5mm-thick blade tackles any outdoor task with ease
  • Black stonewashed finish gives this EDC tool a sleek look
  • Patented Tri-Ad locking mechanism secures the blade in place during use keeping you safe
  • Hand-forged in Italy the home of world-renowned MagnaCut steel
  • Measures 9-3/8″ overall
  • Wt.: 5.2 oz.

products.description:
The Hawkbill Specter boasts a lean lightweight profile that delivers an exceptional in-hand feel and makes it ideal for everyday carry enthusiasts of all kinds. From its 3.8mm-thick 20CV steel blade to the edge-retaining hollow grind and eye-catching matte black PVD finish this knife isn’t just built to do your dirty work it also looks good while it’s at it. What’s more the tool features solid titanium bolsters to give the understructure superior strength from its forged carbon-fiber handle to the 3.8-inch blade’s talon tip ensuring it stands up to any outdoor task you throw at it. And when you pair those rugged good looks and does-it-all construction with an easy-to-operate thumb stud and secure liner lock your peace of mind gets a boost too—because when it comes down to it safety is always paramount. The cherry on top? An integrated clip-up pocket clip that allows for convenient discreet carry all day every day.

  • Boasts a 3.8″ talon-point blade forged from durable 20CV steel
  • Thanks to its hollow grind the blade delivers lasting edge retention
  • Integrated thumb stud makes deployment quick and simple
  • A liner lock secures the blade in place when deployed
  • Forged carbon-fiber handle provides a no-slip ergonomic grip

products.name: AAC Blackout/Breakout Tool
products.description:
This AAC Blackout Flash Hider Installation Tool is an excellent solution for armorers gunsmiths and/or gun enthusiasts to quickly and easily install or remove any 3-Prong Blackout Flash Hider without marring its finish or damaging the teeth of a quick detach silencer interface when applying the required torque for the job. The tool attaches directly to any 3/8″ Drive Tool and incorporates flats for use with a 3/4″ Socket Wrench (both sold separately).

Torque Spec:

  • ½-28 – 20-30 lb-ft
  • 5/8-24 – 45-55 lb-ft
  • ¾-24 – 45-55 lb-ft
  • M15x1 – 30-40 lb-ft
  • .595×32 – 35-45 lb-ft
  • M13x1 LH – 20-30 lb-ft
  • 9/16×24 LH and RH – 30-40 lb-ft

products.name: Springfield Armory Hellcat Hardware Mounting Kit (SHIELD RMSC & JPOINT)
products.description: Hardware for mounting Shield RMSc and JPoint optics to Hellcat OSP. Screws are ready to install without modification. Includes- 2- M4 x .07 x7.5mm screws 2.5mm Allen Key T10 Torx key and instruction card.

products.name: Forster Co-Ax Case and Cartridge Inspector (Pilots Sold Separately)
products.description:
Accurate performance from your ammunition is absolutely dependent on uniformity of both the bullet and the case. Achieving that uniformity is not possible without an accurate reliable measuring device.

Forster’s exclusive Co-Ax Case & Cartridge Inspector provides you with the ability to ensure uniformity by measuring three critical dimensions:

  • Neck wall thickness.
  • Case bullet and cartridge runout (concentricity).

Features:

  • Uniquely supports case/cartridge to check both bullet and case alignment in relation to the centerline (long axis) of the case/cartridge.
  • Measurements are in increments of .001.
  • Accommodates cartridges from 204 Ruger to 45-70.
  • Includes precision dial indicator accurate to .001.
  • Maximum overall case length that may be inspected is 3.50.
  • Quality manufactured from precision-engineered automotive-type castings.
  • Uses the same Pilots as Forster Case Trimmers.
  • (Note: 17 cal. Pilot is not compatible with this tool.)

products.name: Forster Case Neck Graphiter
products.description:
When it comes time to size a fired case the Forster Case Neck Graphiter is an exceptional tool. Typically pulling the expander button through the case causes an issue due to residual deposits being left from firing that create friction when withdrawing the expander. In some cases friction can cause stretching or distortion of the case neck.

While lubrication helps this is not always the solution because of potential gunpowder contamination. With this graphite the problem is resolved. Made from tough and impact-resistant plastic the graphite accommodates .22 to .35 calibers and can be permanently mounted if preferred.

products.name: Forster Powdered Graphite for Case Neck
products.description:
For reducing expander ball friction in the case necks the Forster Powdered Graphite for Case Graphiter is an excellent choice often used by people who do reloading. This particular graphiter consists of three brushes that mount to the base and are capable of handling .22 to .35 caliber ammo.

By moving the case graphiter up and down on a brush you clean as well as lubricate the neck is done. As a result both distortion and stretching are minimized. Included with this product is enough motor mica to process between 2000 and 3000 cases.

products.name: Forster 3-in-1 Case Mouth Cutter for Original or Power Case Trimmer .224 cal
products.description:
Made for various calibers Forster Products 3-in-1 Case Mouth Cutter Carbide helps save valuable time as well as effort during reloading sessions. With this particular product three critical steps for preparing cases are done at once. The main feature of the cutter is the extremely sharp blades made from carbide designed to chamfer case necks inside and outside.

It chamfers the outside of the neck at 30 degrees and on the inside 14 degrees. This cutter also trims brass to the exact length preferred while also deburring. While the pilots can be interchanged you will need to adjust the cutting edge.

products.name: 3-in-1 Case Mouth Cutter with 264 Pilot (for 6.5mm)
products.description: 3-in-1 Case Mouth Cutter with 264 Pilot (for 6.5mm)

products.name: Forster 3-in-1 Case Mouth Cutter for Original or Power Case Trimmer .308 cal
products.description:

products.name: Forster Classic Case Trimmer
products.description:
The Forster Classic Case Trimmer is used for case trimming of larger-caliber cartridges. This trimmer is appropriate for trimming over 200 big bore calibers that range in length between 1 7/8 inches to 4 1/8 inches. Similar to the Original trimmer the Classic model utilizes style collets and calibers specific to pilots of Brown & Sharpe in order to ensure every cut is clean and square.

The base length of this trimmer is 6 1/2-inches and is constructed of aluminum alloy for the base and for the cutter shaft steel alloy. For shorter trimmed cases the standard length base can be added.

products.name: Forster Original Case Trimmer
products.description:
The Forster Original Case Trimmer is the ideal choice for trimming cases from .17 caliber all the way to .458 caliber. This trimmer can accommodate diameters from .171 to .459 inches as well as cartridges that are no greater than 2.94 inches.

Used by people who enjoy reloading this trimmer is made to trim brass cases with precision and according to specifications. As a fine mini-lathe the trimmer uses the same type of collets as a Brown & Sharpe. If needed trimmers for shorter and longer cases are sold separately.

products.name: Cutter Shaft for Original Case Trimmer
products.description: Cutter Shaft for Original Case Trimmer

products.name: Forster Case Trimmer Pilot #17
products.description:
The Forster Case Trimmer Pilot is an inexpensive item used for home reloading and made for Original Classic and Power Forster Cast Trimmers including all of the popular calibers. When choosing the correct trimmer pilot it is imperative to purchase the right diameter. This is the inside of the neck diameter after full-length sizing of brass.

The diameter of the trimmer pilot needed will be just slightly less than the actual diameter of the bullet. For assistance in choosing the appropriate size trimmer pilot information is provided on the Forster website.

products.name: Forster Case Trimmer Pilot -#2 - .22 cal (.223-.224" dia)
products.description:
Extremely affordable the Forster Power Case Trimmer Pilot - #2 - .22 cal (.223-.224" dia) precisely grinds cases to 0.005 inches smaller than the bullet diameter and trims them perfectly square.

To use this trimmer pilot the screw set in the cutter shaft is loosened the pilot is placed in the shaft then the screw is tightened. By using this pilot bullets are not released too soon which causes bullet-to-bore misalignment and affects overall accuracy. Rather than case necks being of different thicknesses they are uniform. With this bullets fire appropriately for outstanding performance.

products.name: Forster Trimmer Collet for Original Case Trimmer #1
products.description:
The Forster Classic Case Trimmer Collet is available in four different options including #5 #6 #7 and #8. All of these collets are affordably priced and built to last. Using the #8 as an example a reloader is required along with the Forster Classic Case Trimmer in order to trim specific cartridges.

One note: This collet is not designed to work with the Original or Power Case Trimmer. As far as cartridge sizes for the #8 these include 280 Nitro Express Rimmed Flanged 38-56 Winchester 40-65 Winchester 40-90 Sharps Bottle Neck 45-100 Sharps Straight 45-70 Government and 45-90 Winchester.

products.name: Forster Long Case Trimmer Base 6-1/2"
products.description:
The Forster Long Case Trimmer Base 6-1/2" is a replacement part that is high quality and affordable. This trimmer base is an excellent addition for people who do reloading on a bench using the Original or Classic Case Trimmer manufactured by Forster. For someone who needs a solid base for trimming longer brass pieces this is an excellent choice.

The base trimmer measures 6.5 inches and works great for brass pieces that measure between 1 7/8 to 4 1/8 inches. Made from aluminum alloy the base is both strong and durable.

products.name: Forster Case Trimmer Cutter Shaft for Original Case Trimmer .17 cal
products.description: The Forster Case Trimmer Cutter Shaft - .17 caliber is made to do most of a Forster Case Trimmer.

products.name: Forster Original Case Trimmer Kit (Includes 6 Pilots & 3 Collets)
products.description:
This Forster Case Trimmer Kit (w/6 Pilots & 3 Collets) is the original which comes with six pilots including 22 24 25 27 28 and 30 as well as three collets of 1 2 and 3. For most calibers with bullet dimensions ranging from 0.171 to 0.459 inches this is ideal. The kit boasts a premium shell holder design as well.

Collets 1 through 4 fit the original case trimmer while holding rims of most pistol and rifle calibers in that very range. This kit is an excellent choice for expanding on an existing reloading system.

products.name: Forster Inside/Outside Deburring Tool .17 to .45 cal
products.description:
For reloading enthusiasts Forster is known for quality as with the Forster Deburring Tool. This is an inexpensive double-ended multifunction tool that can be used with a lathe attached to the end of a Deburring Tool Base or by hand. With this tool chamfering and eliminating burrs from both inside and outside of the case mouth is done quickly.

This deburring tool is made specifically for calibers that range between .17 and .45. This tool is also well-constructed made from quality materials and made to provide years of seamless service.

products.name: Forster Hand Held Outside Neck Turner
products.description:
The Forster Hand Held Outside Neck Turner allows a reloader to ensure the bullet is released consistently from the case neck. During one part of the ignition the neck needs to expand releasing the bullet. If one side of the neck is thicker the thinner side will cause the bullet to release early which causes a slight misalignment of bullet-to-bore that has a major impact on accuracy.

With this turner case necks have uniform thickness thanks to the carbide cutter which is precision ground. In addition the micrometer knob makes adjustments to 0.0005 inches in either direction.

products.name: Forster Handheld Outside Neck Turner Pilot .224"
products.description:
The Forster Hand Outside Neck Pilot is designed for people who do reloading and want a guarantee that the bullet will be released in a consistent manner from the case neck. At ignition it is imperative for the case neck to expand allowing the release of the bullet. If one side of the neck is thicker than another the bullet will release prematurely causing a misalignment of bullet-to-bore.

When this occurs accuracy is dramatically impacted. Mandrels which are the steel points are ground 0.002 to 0.025 inches smaller than the diameter of the bullet providing excellent performance.

products.name: Forster Hollow Pointer 1/16
products.description:
The Forster Hollow Pointer is available in 1/8 and 1/16 inches and made from high-quality materials and workmanship that guarantee top performance. This pointer is not to be used with jacket bullets regardless of type but for people who do home reloading it is ideal for drilling out hollow cavities in the noses of cast bullets.

With the stop collar on the case trimmer set the depth of the hollow point is controlled. For extremely short and long rounds a short or long trimmer base may be required. As with all Forster products this pointer is high quality.

products.name: Forster Hollow Pointer 1/8
products.description:

With the stop collar on the case trimmer set the depth of the hollow point is controlled. For extremely short and long rounds a short or long trimmer base may be required. As with all Forster products this pointer is high quality.

products.name: Forster Neck Reamer #17
products.description:
The Forster Neck Reamer comes in a variety of diameters including .224 .243 .264 .284 .308 .429 and many others. When reloading if the case neck is too thick it can put pressure on the chamber and cause flyers. By mounting this neck reamer in the Case Trimmer rather than the pilot it helps eliminate excess brass from the walls of the neck.

This particular neck reamer grinds the entire bullet diameter to precision creating perfect symmetry. Made from strong and durable steel the reamer is designed for unsized and untrimmed fired cases.

This particular neck reamer grinds the entire bullet diameter to precision creating perfect symmetry. Made from strong and durable steel the reamer is designed for unsized and untrimmed fired cases.

products.name: Forster Neck Tension Gage - NTG-224
products.description:
Use the Neck Tension Gage (NTG) as an inspection tool to quickly and accurately screen/sort a batch of brass before your bullet seating operation.

The NTG provides reloaders with the information needed to create exacting neck tensions during the bullet seating operation.

  • Use after case neck sizing and before bullet seating to help determine optimal inside neck diameter for consistent release of a bullet from your reloaded rounds.
  • Allows for inspection of the inside diameters of case necks to be sure a “donut” has not formed at the neck-shoulder junction.

Available in five calibers the NTG Neck Tension Gage Inspection Tool consists of four stepped diameters that increase in size until reaching the handle. Each diameter is etched on the metal tool.

Simply insert the stepped end of the tool into the neck of your sized case sliding it in until one of the diameters achieves a slip fit in the case neck. Use the resulting value to fine-tune your case preparation.

products.name: Forster Outside Neck Turner Accessory for Original Case Trimmer (Pilots Sold Separately)
products.description:
The Forster Outside Neck Turner Accessory for Original Case Trimmer is unique because rather than being centered on the pilot only as with handheld turners the case is turned concentric to true axis. With this turner neck walls are made of uniform thickness as well as the same outside diameter.

When adjusted properly this turner reaches a tolerance of 0.0001 inches. In addition the cutter head is designed with a circular carbide cutter that can easily be adjusted. The feed rate is controllable simply by rotating the feeder cam while the length of the cut is controlled with a mechanical stop.

products.name: Forster Outside Neck Turner Pilot #243
products.description:
Made specifically for .243 diameter this Forster Outside Neck Turner Pilot #243 is an exceptional buy for someone who does home reloading. To ensure accuracy when firing a bullet must have the same neck thickness. In order to expand properly and avoid a bullet-to-bore misalignment this pilot creates wall thickness of the same size.

A goal of reloading is to have consistency in your ammunition and with this pilot that is made possible. The mandrels are evenly ground to 0.002 to 0.0025 inches smaller than the diameter of the bullet which boosts performance.

products.name: Forster Outside Neck Turner Pilot #263
products.description:
Available in various diameters the Forster Outside Neck Turner Pilot is affordable. For someone who enjoys reloading this pilot guarantees consistent release of the bullet from the case neck. In order for the bullet to release at the point of ignition the neck has to expand.

If the side of the case neck is thicker on one side the bullet will release too soon causing misalignment of bullet-to-bore that will affect accuracy. This pilot grinds the steel points which are known as mandrels to 0.002 to 0.0025 inches smaller than the diameter of the bullet for the best performance.

products.name: Forster Outside Neck Turner Pilot #308
products.description:
Available in various diameters the Forster Outside Neck Turner Pilot is affordable. For someone who enjoys reloading this pilot guarantees consistent release of the bullet from the case neck. In order for the bullet to release at the point of ignition the neck has to expand.

products.name: Forster Power Adapter For Original or Classic Case Trimmer
products.description:
As with all Forster products the Forster Power Adapter For Case Trimmer is made from quality materials and is affordably priced. With this adapter any hand trimmer can be transformed into a power trimmer. The adapter is made to fit the Original Classic and .50 BMG case trimmers.

The handle is simply removed from the trimmer and replaced with this adapter. Using a power drill or electric screwdriver is all that is required for power. In addition the stop collar and cutter shaft do not change allowing accurate case length settings to be perfectly maintained.

products.name: Forster Center for Primer Pocket Cleaner & Primer Pocket Chamfering Tool
products.description:
The Forster Center for Pocket Cleaner/Chamfering Tool is a case prep tool used for Forster Original and Classic case trimmers. This tool gets the job done quickly and with outstanding results far better than prepping by hand. For reloading each case must be in excellent condition and this tool ensures that.

This tool is designed to mount in the collet side of the trimmer which provides support to the case mouth. To use the tool hold the case mouth over the center tool with one hand and operate the cleaner or chamfer with the other by turning the crank.

products.name: Forster Primer Pocket Chamfering Tool
products.description:
The Forster Primer Pocket Chamfering Tool is made from steel and designed to last. With this tool someone who enjoys reloading can chamfer thousands of cases with complete consistency. In addition uniformity and depth are controlled simply by setting the stop collar.

To use this chamfering tool the case mouth is held over the primer pocket center and the crimp removed by turning the trimmer handle all without using collets. You will see consistent ignition as well as less occurrence of misfires since primer and powder residue from the case pockets will be eliminated.

products.name: Forster Stuck Case Remover
products.description:
The Forster s Case Remover is great for people who do home reloading. Developed as an inexpensive and easy-to-use case remover it works on any size die as long as it has threaded spindles. With this design stuck cases with the de-capping rod and expander ball lodged in the die can be dislodged.

All of the components of this case remover are hardened to ensure a long life. In addition the cleaner comes with a washer that helps protect the top portion of the die. Forster recommends using this cleaner for .22 through .50 caliber dies.

products.name: Flitz Knife Restoration Kit
products.description: The Flitz Knife Restoration Kit hits all the needs for knife and outdoor enthusiasts. Kit includes Flitz Liquid Polish Flitz Microfiber Cloth a DMT Knife Sharpener and one bottle of Safariland Lubricating Oil.

products.name: Tru-Fire Draw Check Tool - Standard Size
products.description:
The TruFire Draw Check Tool eliminates accidents caused by dry firing a bow. Used to safely adjust draw length peep sights or any other adjustments. Made in the USA.

Standard Size

products.name: Schrade Rage Phantom Enrage 6 Knife - Replaceable Blade
products.description:
Bringing together one of America’s longest-lasting cutlery companies with the best-selling broadhead of all time the Schrade Enrage Series provides an extremely functional and useful line of replaceable blade knives. Designed with Rage Broadhead Technology Enrage Replacement Blade Knives are razor sharp and designed to endure. Perfect for breaking down a trophy or for those who desire an extremely sharp everyday carry blade The Schrade and Rage Enrage Series has an option for users of all walks.

Engineered to sever the thoughts of conventional replacement blade knife technology the Enrage trio of knives bring together the best of both worlds from Rage and Schrage. Capitalizing on the design of the widely-popular Rage Trypan broadhead blades each knife features a uniquely-designed scalpel-sharp .024” blade system custom-designed to fit the Enrage series of knives. This exclusive 420a stainless steel blade concept offers a narrow point and up to 20% more cutting edge than comparable models. In an effort to solve problems commonly associated with replaceable blade knife concepts a proprietary locking system keeps the blades in place no matter the torque or pressure placed upon the locking mechanism. Driven by an Ultra-Glide steel bearing system Engage knives open easily with the flip of a finger yet stay lock-tight when engaged to offer a rigid backbone that help get the job done — in the field or while at work.

The Phantom Enrage series offered in the Phantom 6 and Phantom 7 which feature a single-sided 2X2 carbon fiber handle with steel locking frame and a 2.25” and 2.63” blade respectively.

Adding to each knives’ versatility is a tight-gripping pocket clip that makes carry easy and secure. Enrage 7 and 8 models will include a custom sheath purpose-built to both the knife and blade case while Enrage 6 models feature only the pocket clip for a more streamlined carry solution.

Designed for those who demand the most from their equipment the Enrage series an ideal option for hunting fishing utility and everyday carry. Included with each model are six replacement blades and a dual-sided storage case featuring a blade removal tool and blade storage compartment.

  • Custom Enrage Replaceable Blade
  • Ultra Glide Bearings
  • Frame Lock
  • Premium Carbon Fiber Handle
  • Pocket Clip
  • Dual-Sided Blade Case
  • Sheath

products.name: Blue Force Gear Helium Whisper Trauma Kit Now! - Coyote Brown
products.description:
Features:

 

  • Size: 2.5" x 4.5" x 7"
  • 3 x 3 MOLLE field required
  • Build: CORDURA ballistic nylon
  • MOLLE compatible Helium Whisper attachment system
  • ULTRAcomp high performance laminate
  • Cross indicator on top flap can be switched to black or left out
  • Our Ball Loaded Index Point or BLIP for short is a feature found on all our lidded pouches and select plate carriers like the Trauma Kit NOW!. BLIP was born in the freezing rain on a Blackwater range. It was there we realized that when you cant feel your fingers its very difficult to get a grasp on a flat piece of webbing and distinguish a pull tab. The ball doesnt rely on friction; the bones in your fingers positively engage it. BLIPs form is both easy to pull and impossible to miss.

products.name: Blue Force Gear Tourniquet NOW! Strap Tourniquet Holder Black
products.description:
The most effective and simplest life-saving tourniquet holder on the market. Every warrior no matter what field of operation should have at least one tourniquet available. The Tourniquet NOW! Strap provides a low profile secure and quickly accessible TQ holder that can be mounted on any MOLLE platform. The elastic loops can fit a variety of NATO style tourniquets such as the SOF-T C-A-T and other similar sized tourniquets.

Specs:

  • Compatibility: Works as a SOF-T to CAT tourniquet holder. Holds Similar Sized TQs and items
  • Installation: 3 Vertical MOLLE Fields
  • Size: 125" x 1" x 4.75"
  • Material: Molded plastic base heavy duty elastic retention loops

products.name: Glock Entrenching Tool Folding Shovel with Saw Black Bulk
products.description:
Entrenching tool folding professional glock shovel made of hardened steel spoon. Ultra durable telescopic stylus allows you to adjust the length in the range of 46-63cm.

Entrenching Tool - folding professional Glock shovel from a Austrian famous weapon manufacturer Glock Company. A robust durable compact size tool designed for professionals.

Spoon - made of black oxidised tempered steel. Lightweight ultra-strong telescopic handle with non-slip structure made of polymer used in the production of components for Glock pistols. Telescopic design allows you to adjust the length of the stylus in the range of 46 cm - 63 cm thereby increasing the comfort of work. The distinguishing feature of the Glock shovel from among others on the market is the largest diameter of the handle that allows a comfortable and save grip.

The construction of the shovel allows you to use the tool as a shovel spade or as a hoe (the ability to work under three different angles). To do this block the shovel spoon in one of three positions. In addition the Entrenching Tool shovel is equipped with a large efficient wood saw inside the blade spade made of hardened steel.

products.name: Glock Field Knife 6-1/2" Clip Point Blade Black Grey with Saw Bulk
products.description:
The Glock Field Knife features a tough full tang carbon steel clip point blade with a integrated saw on its upper edge and a molded polymer hilt. The set includes an integral retention system to keep the GLOCK knife secure during times of extreme activity.

  • Perfectly balanced for hand-to-hand combat
  • Phosphate treated and coated corrosion-resistant blade
  • One-piece polymer sheath Gray polymer handle and gray sheath
  • 6 1/2 inch carbon steel clip point blade and molded polymer hilt tough enough to break windows or cut through the toughest tree limb yet perfectly balanced for appropriate conditions.

products.name: Glock Entrenching Tool Pkg'd
products.description:
The Glock Entrenching Tool is a multipurpose tool that is designed to perform a variety of essential outdoor functions. This tool features a telescopic handle and a foldable blade that can be locked into four positions. The blade is made from hardened steel protected by a black anticorrosive coating and features a sharpened edge.

Because the Glock Entrenching Tool doesn't have any welding or rivets in its design it is much stronger and more durable than comparable tools. This tool comes with a steel saw that has a screwdriver tip that is stored right in the handle of the tool. What more could you ask for?

products.name: Glock Field Knife / Saw Back - Flat Dark Earth (Pkg'd)
products.description: The Glock Field Knife / Saw Back survival knife is a perfect addition to any tool kit field pack or belt. Developed in close cooperation with Austrian Army Rangers the no-nonsense GLOCK knife features a tough 6 1/2 inch carbon steel clip point blade and molded polymer hilt tough enough to break windows or cut through the toughest tree limb yet perfectly balanced for appropriate conditions. The one-piece polymer sheath is ideal for keeping the 3/16 inch blade protected. The set includes an integral retention system to keep your GLOCK knife secure during times of extreme activity. Fits up to 2-1/2" belt.

products.name: Muddy Boot Glove Dryer Collapsible
products.description:
Wet boots? Soggy gloves? Get ‘em dry and do it fast in as little as an hour or two with Muddy’s adjustable Boot and Glove Dryer. Not only does it accommodate everything from tall rubber boots to standard height boots shoes and even gloves but this dryer also maintains a steady 104°F temperature to ensure a gentle dry that won’t damage your most trusted pairs of cold-weather hunting gear. Warmed by a quiet drying fan with a high-quality motor and easy-to-operate turn knob display the unit boasts a built-in 3-hour shutoff as well as overheat protection so you don’t have to worry about it reaching unsafe temps when it’s out of sight and out of mind. Plus thanks to a retractable tube design foldable blower outlets and integrated power cord storage space on the underside of the machine it accommodates a variety of foot and handwear while remaining extremely quick to pack away and convenient to store—even during travel—thanks to its compact size.

  • Retractable tube design adjusts to accommodate boots up to 17" in height
  • Removes moisture to prevent odor and improve the longevity of boots shoes gloves and other gear
  • Maintains a temperature of 104°F thanks to a warm forced-air drying fan
  • Protective integrated shutoff mechanism after 3 hours eliminates worry of overheating
  • Adjustable runtime allows the dryer to operate for up to 3 hours
  • Motor runs quietly and is operated via a turn knob display
  • Foldable blower outlets and hidden cord storage space make it compact and easy to store

products.name: Muddy Nucleus Heated Hand Muff Brown Clay One Size
products.description: Part of Muddy’s all-new assortment of whitetail hunting apparel and accessories every item with the Nucleus name delivers a long-lasting and adjustable heat source that sees passionate tree stand hunters through their longest coldest days in the field. And because there’s nothing die-hard whitetail hunters love more than lightweight dual-purpose gear the Nucleus Heated Hand Muff/Seat is the perfect complementary accessory to the whole battery-powered line. It boasts a durable webbed waist strap with snap-buckle closure that adjusts to accommodate forward and backward-facing wear—serving as either a hand muff or a seat warmer. Thanks to the three heat settings users can warm themselves through any weather conditions adjusting the temp as they see fit. Simply press the easy-to-access power button on the front of the pouch to choose between low medium or high modes and enjoy the added warmth delivered by the included 10000mAh battery. A super-soft fleece construction with a highly water-repellent shell allows you to adapt quickly to the elements.

products.name: Muddy Insulated Hand Muff Mossy Oak Bottomland
products.description: The warmth-retaining Insulated Hand Muff is the perfect insulating addition to your mid to late-season hunting attire. It features a brushed tricot outer shell with super-soft tricot lining and quick-drying polyfill insulation. Thanks to the ergonomic shape complete with elasticized fleece-lined cuffs the muff conforms to your body’s natural positioning when in the stand or seated in the timber sealing in warmth. An adjustable webbed waist belt with buckle closure provides a personalized fit that can quickly be adjusted to accommodate your layering system as it changes with the weather. One stretch front and one back zippered pocket secure gear and accessories so you remain focused on the most important task: hunting.

products.name: Muddy Overshoe Foot Warmer Brown Clay 2XL 12-15
products.description:
When the winds whip and temps plummet body heat is rapidly lost through your extremities causing hands and feet to feel painfully cold fast. Muddy's neoprene Overshoe Foot Warmers are a surefire way to keep your feet warm and protected during long stationary sits in the coldest stretch of the season. These highly packable heat-retaining covers fit over even the most insulated pair of winter boots. Ideal for outdoor activities requiring little to no movement like ice fishing sitting in a deer stand or even attending cold-weather sporting events these bootie covers are windproof water-resistant and rated for when temps dip down to 25°F and colder meaning you’ll not only stay warmer than you would without them but far drier and more motivated too. Each includes an integrated exterior pocket designed specifically for holding disposable hand warmers providing added warmth during long days when your dogs need it most.

  • Heat-retaining neoprene construction is perfect for stationary activities like tree stand hunting ice fishing and more
  • Meant to wear over any pair of winter boots to prevent loss of body heat through your feet
  • Fully windproof and water-resistant to ensure feet stay dry through it all
  • Side gussets stretch easily making them simple to slide on and off
  • Rated to keep feet warm and protected in temps dipping to 25°F and below
  • Exterior hand warmer pockets deliver additional warmth to overshoes and wearers’ boots on the coldest days
  • Includes two disposable Muddy hand warmers
  • Thin grip bottoms provide long-lasting durability 
  • Booties are highly packable making them a breeze to transport anywhere you need them
  • For use during stationary outdoor activities only not meant for hiking

products.name: Honeywell North 5400 Series Full Face Respirator Mask with Dual Cartridge Connectors for N Series Filters M/L
products.description:
The Honeywell 5400 Series is the ideal workhorse respirator for subcontractors and other occasional users. The facepiece is made from a soft thermoplastic elastomer that fits comfortably and is latex free. With a wide sealing area the mask fits a variety of facial types. The polycarbonate lens offers a 200° field of vision and downward view for optimal sight in all directions. The lens is also designed to withstand high impact thereby eliminating the need for additional eye protection. The 5400 Series facepiece provides the integral features needed for compliance.

  • Lens offers 200° of vision
  • Nose cup standard
  • Reduces fogging and increases worker comfort
  • The best value you can find in a full facepiece
  • Honeywell innovation: quality and attention to detail come together in an economically priced mask

products.name: Howard Leight Safety Single Pack PPE Kit Face Mask Gloves & Cleansing Wipes
products.description:
Enhance peace of mind for yourself and those around you with the Honeywell Safety Pack. This Honeywell PPE Kit is available in a resealable pouch that allows for convenient on the go access. Keep Honeywell Personal Protective Equipment in your car purse work bag backpack at the home for guests or anywhere else you’ll need them. Having the right equipment and solutions allows us to adapt to our new normal ensuring that we’re on the correct path to returning to work returning to life and reshaping the future as we know it – together.

Comfortable Fit

A comfortable face mask is less likely to be removed or adjusted during wear. These 3-ply face masks are lightweight for comfort during extended wear and pleated for easy expansion to fit most adult face sizes.

Surface Contact Avoidance

You can avoid directly touching surfaces and handling objects outside the home with non-sterile gloves. These gloves offer excellent versatility for performing everyday tasks. They're lightweight comfortable and latex-free.

Easy Surface Cleaning

Cleaning wipes offer a convenient solution for wiping down frequently touched out-of-home surfaces. These can include office door handles smart phones and your car's steering wheel.

Resealable Pouch

Avoid exposing your PPE to keys cash and coins when carrying it loosely on your person. The safety pack comes in a secure resealable pouch. This allows you to keep all of your PPE items organized and separated from your other belongings providing easy access when you need it.

Convenient Storage

The compact size of the Honeywell Safety Pack allows for convenient carrying and storage almost anywhere. If you're out walking the pouch easily fits into a purse handbag or backpack. You can also store it in a glove compartment or center console when driving.

  • This kit comes in an easy-to-open resealable pouch for your convenient access to the contents.
  • PPE safety pack contains: (1) face mask (1) pair of non-latex non-sterile gloves and (2) cleaning wipes.
  • Face Mask: 3 ply pleated lightweight material.
  • Gloves: Non-latex non-sterile. One size fits most adults.
  • Cleaning Wipes: % Alcohol > 60% Ethanol.
  • Safety Packs assembled in the U.S. with U.S. and imported components.

products.name: Mark 7 Power Trim Express Press Mounted High Speed Case Trimmer
products.description:
The new Power Trim Xpress case trimmer will tackle the toughest commercial trimming jobs yet and is priced to fit any reloaders' budget. The trimmer features a powerful variable speed DC motor yet it is also a slim design that takes up minimal room - only one die station on progressive presses unlike other trimmers that take up two or three stations!
The trimmer will speed through standard trim jobs and also easily handle cartridge conversions such as 223 to 300 Blackout.
The Power Trim Xpress accepts standard trim dies and is equipped with a vacuum manifold to cleanly evacuate chips. In addition the trimmer comes with a long-lasting carbide cutter.

Features:

  • Electric Press Mounted Case Trimmer
  • Slim motor design takes up minimal room
  • 1-1/2” vacuum manifold to evacuate chips
  • Powerful industrial grade variable speed DC motor
  • Replaceable carbide cutter
  • Uses standard Trim-Dies
  • Trims and case forms 300 Blackout from .223 brass with one stroke!

products.name: Mero 550 Paracord - 100' 550 lb Black
products.description:
Strong durable and lightweight quick drying and rot resistant. This braid is very popular and is the commercial version of the original parachute cords used by the military first developed for parachutes during WW2. The 7-2 ply strand core can be removed and used in survival situations. Sheath is composed of 32 woven strands. The high tensile strength is a plus when you?re out in the field or at home. Patterns are sharp and vibrant. A must have for any outdoorsman or any home. Ideal for survival emergency kits shelters snares fishing trapping handle wraps defense first aid fire bow and more.

  • 500 lb. tensile strength 550 Type II Commercial quality 100 percent woven nylon.
  • 7 2-strand core
  • 5/32 in diameter
  • Made in America by a certified government contractor

products.name: Berry's Rotary Brass Sorter / Media Separator
products.description:
Berry's Products have given you the ability to separate your media and sort your brass with the Berry's Rotary Brass Sorter / Media Separator.

The little blue knob in the center of the black basket allows you to change the size of the grate depending on what caliber you want to sort 1st (hint: start with the smallest caliber).

Once set repeat the step on the other side of the basket then close the outer clam shell.

Now rotate and you will hear your sorted brass falling out.

Never again will you have to hand sort an entire bucket of range brass or make a mess with a pan sorter. From one reloader to another this product is well worth the price!!

products.name: Berry's Rotary Brass/Media Separator Basket (Only)
products.description: Berry's Rotary Media Separator provides an easy way to separate your tumbled brass from media in one clean operation. From measuring environmental data during cargo transport to conditions in the field for military training to feeling secure about the climate conditions in any room shipped box cargo trailer freight container to as simple as a room in your home or office building you are able to measure all of these conditions even when you?re physically not there.

It is built with laminated Squadron fabrics and can provide content protection against scuffs and scrapes.

products.name: Kestrel 2500NV Weather Meter / Digital Altimeter +NV Backlight - Olive Drab
products.description:
The Kestrel 2500NV takes the great features of the Kestrel 2000 and adds in a pressure sensor.  Predict fish and wildlife activity as well as when bad weather is headed your way with the three-hour pressure trend indicator. With its easy-to-use digital pressure altimeter you have the perfect instrument for any outdoor activity - get conditions in seconds right in the palm of your hand. In addition to predicting weather activity barometric pressure also influences a bullet’s trajectory which is why the Kestrel 2500NV is used by shooters and hunters when accuracy is important.

Note: The Kestrel 2500NV has a night-vision preserving backlight which helps users to sustain natural night vision. The NV's backlight incorporates an optical filter to reduce overall brightness and minimize blue and green spectrum light to preserve night vision. Additionally NV backlights are also much dimmer than a standard backlight making it more difficult to detect with the naked eye in night operations. This backlight appears soft greyish pink not red and is still in the visible spectrum so it is not compatible with night-vision equipment.

It takes 30 to 45 minutes for the average eye to adapt to darkness and maximize night vision. Even a short burst of white yellow green or blue light “bleaches out” the rod cell photoreceptors in the eye and causes night blindness until the entire adaptation process can take place again. Light in the red spectrum does not cause this “bleaching out” preventing night blindness and night vision fatigue.

Kestrel Weather & Environmental Meters are designed & manufactured in the U.S.A and are backed by our 5-year warranty. Innovatively designed for stability and accuracy in abrupt condition changes. Rugged and durable Kestrels are drop tested waterproof and designed to float if dropped in water.

  • 3-Button Control
  • Backlight - Night Vision Preserving Light Red
  • Data Hold Function
  • Date & Time
  • Drop-Tested to MIL-STD-810G
  • Hard Slip-On Protective Cover
  • High Contrast Sunlight Readable Monochrome LCD Display
  • Minimum/Maximum/Average Reading
  • Pressure Sensor
  • Temperature Sensor (Patented External Isolated)
  • Waterproof to IP67 (3'/1M for 30 minutes)

Includes :

  • Battery - 1 x CR2032
  • Certificate Of Conformity (Spec Sheet)
  • Instructions
  • Lanyard
  • Protective Cover - Hard Slip-on

products.name: Kestrel 2700 Ballistics Weather Meter with LiNK - Tan
products.description:
The Kestrel 2700 Ballistics Weather Meter sets the standard for long-range accuracy reliability and affordability. Combining onsite wind and weather measurements with an accurate ballistics solver - the 2700 delivers precise firing solutions for dead-on aim at long-distance targets. From youth hunters to the lifelong outdoorsmen the Kestrel 2700 eliminates the guesswork allowing you to be confident in a clean shot on the first-round.

  • Accurate Environmentals - Measures wind speed and direction temperature and altitude
  • G1/G7 Ballistics Solver - Large library of independently tested bullet data
  • User-Friendly - Simple 3 button operation and Easy Mode step-by-step guidance on getting started
  • Rugged All-Weather Durability - IP-67 Waterproof MIL-STD-810 drop-tested and backed by Mfg. 5-Year Warranty
  • Protective Slip-On Cover - Slides over the entire unit for added durability
  • Load & Go Convenience - Set up in the gun profiles via the app then leave your phone behind - the 2700 is fully functional as a stand-alone field tool
  • App Supported Option with LiNK - Easily build store and transfer gun and bullet data to and from unit
  • Max Range - 875 yds
Environmental Measures
  Station Pressure (Absolute Pressure)
  Temperature
  Wind Direction
  Wind Speed/Air Speed

products.name: Kestrel 5700 Elite Weather Meter with Applied Ballistics with LiNK - Black
products.description:
Kestrel 5700 Video HERE

The Kestrel Elite Weather Meter with Applied Ballistics is referred to as the Kestrel 5700 Elite. With the addition of the Bluetooth Kestrel LINK functionality you'll want to download the Kestrel LiNK Ballistics app to your smart phone to load your guns / ammo to the meter. The Kestrel Meters with Bluetooth include the software necessary to communicate wirelessly at a range of up to 100 feet with a clear line of site (walls or obstacles will effect this range).

Kestrel 5700 Elite Weather Meter with Applied Ballistics with integrated Bluetooth technology offer the ultimate in portable and accurate environmental data. Now both real-time and logged data can be transferred wirelessly and automatically to a MAC/PC or Smartphone or iPhone. It also connects via LiNK to the Bushnell CONX Range Finder where you can view results from the AB Kestrel right on your Range Finder. There will be more rangefinders and scopes down the line that will connect directly with the Kestrel meters.

  • Better PC application for ease of building library
  • Crosswind Jump: truing in winds without it can give you an errant MV
  • If you calibrate in one environment and move to a drastically different environment the device will adjust automatically
  • Able to export the windage elevation wind speed via BT to an external device

products.name: Kestrel 5700 Ruger Ballistics Weather Meter w/ Applied Ballistics & LiNK Black
products.description:
The Kestrel 5700 Ballistics Weather Meter measures wind altitude and all critical weather and ballistic variables to calculate an accurate aim point for long-range shooting. No more DOPE cards re-zeroing or guessing at the wind. This all-in-one compact tool combines onsite environmental measurements with a powerful G1/G7 ballistics calculator to deliver precise elevation and windage solutions for any gun any round any shot. Get first-shot confidence with the all-in-one long range shooting solution trusted by long range hunters and shooters. Includes 1 AA battery Certificate of Conformity (spec sheet) Instructions Lanyard and protective drawstring pouch.

The Kestrel 5700 Ruger Ballistics Software is preloaded with a Ruger RPR 6.5 Creed with the Hornady 40 gr ELDM. When you open the app it jumps into a custom gun building that has full details on various Ruger rifles and various ammo loads. You are still able to build other guns in both the app and the units as well.

The Kestrel 5700 has ballistics software but it's not Applied Ballistics. If you want the best get the Elite. FYI - You can upgrade to the Elite.

  • LiNK - It only comes with LiNK which is where you'll get any firmware updates.
  • DSF - It does not have Drop Scale Factor so if you are shooting transonic (past 1200 yards) do not get this meter get the Elite. Shooting less than 1200 it won't matter.
  • CUSTOM CURVES- The Elite has the custom curves. The 5700 does NOT. People who rely on G1 / G7 rely on what the bullet manufacturer wants you to believe and is on the box. Sometimes this is marketing by the manufacturer. Companies are known to fudge there G7 factors to make it sound better than it is against the competition.The Custom curves have been tested and proven. They are measurements to a specific bullet so there is a lot of value to someone who cares. This has tremendous value which is what costs you $300 more for the Elite but will easily save you that in bullets over time.

products.name: Kestrel 5700 Ballistics Weather Meter with Hornady 4DOF LiNK
products.description:
For Precision & Competitive Shooting - The Kestrel with Hornady 4DOF quickly and accurately determines long range holdovers and windage corrections to get you on target with first round hits. This all-in-one unit combines real-time environmental measurements with the 4DOF ballistics calculator for a rugged and dependable compact yet powerful long-range shooting tool. No more DOPE cards guessing at the wind or being unsure where your bullet will hit when you change elevation.

Environmental Measures :

  • Altitude (Barometric)

  • Compass Direction
  • Crosswind
  • Density Altitude

  • Heat Stress Index
  • Relative Humidity
  • Station Pressure (Absolute Pressure)
  • Temperature
  • Wet Bulb Temperature (Psychrometric)
  • Wind Chill
  • Wind Speed/Air Speed

products.name: Kestrel Rotating Vane Mount & Carry Case for Kestrel 5000 Series - Black Series BLK
products.description:
A lot of thought was put into making this vane mount for the 5000 Kestrel series . It's simpler design than the last and much more durable. The meter snaps right into it and will mount to any tripod or other 1/4-20 fitted bracket allowing use of an extension pole for taking wind or air flow readings. This turns your Kestrel into a full-featured weather station with a large wind vane and precision pivot that keeps the Kestrel oriented into the wind for continuous measurement and logging of wind speed wind direction and all other key weather parameters.

Note: These are included with the 5400 LINK & 5500 LINK models.

Includes Vane Mount Pouch that will fit both your Kestrel 5000 series meter and the Vane Mount. An internal battery loop (as well as little pocket) secures extra AA batteries and a snap-strap on the rear secures the kit to your belt or pack. The idea here is you have a portable weather station.

Vane Mount Kit in case :

  • Weight: 10.5 ounces / 295 grams
  • Size: 2.5 x 3 x 8.5 inches / 6.5 x 7.5 x 22 cm

Includes adjustable clamp compatible with all Kestrel Meters. Ideal for Kestrel Rotating Vane Mount accessory. Three section legs with flip lever locks and non-marring rubber feet. This tri-pod extends 20.5 - 52" and weighs 2.3 lbs.

products.name: Kershaw Fire Starter
products.description:
Get a Kershaw magnesium alloy Fire Starter when rain snow or whatever Mother Nature dishes it out.

The firesteel shaft is good for up to 3000 strikes and the chrome-plated striker is easy to hold and use. A molded plastic handle makes it easy to use and a nylon cord keeps it handy when you need it. To get your fire going all you’ll need is a small pile of dry grass wood shavings or other flammable materials. Hold the magnesium firesteel shaft close to the pile and quickly draw the striker down the shaft at a right angle to produce sparks. The sparks will ignite the dry materials and as the fire becomes established you will be able to gradually add larger materials to the fire until it is at the desired size. The Kershaw Fire Starter also lights camp stoves and gas barbeques. In an emergency the brilliant spark can be used as an emergency signal.

The Fire Starter itself is compact enough to fit comfortably in your driest pocket - and of course it makes an essential addition to your dry-box supplies or survival gear.

products.name: Kershaw Cinder Keychain Knife - 1.4" Blade
products.description:
Then what you need is a knife that still has plenty of style and cutting power but in a smaller ?key chain? size.

The Cinder is small enough to attach to your keychain yet it?s still capable of doing most of the tasks you carry a knife for. From opening packages to breaking down boxes the Cinder?s got you covered. What?s more you know the Cinder is built for performance. For one thing it?s designed by Rick Hinderer well known for the real-world practicality of his knife designs. For another it?s precision manufactured by Kershaw known for our top-notch fit and finish.

The blade is just 1.4 inches long but because of the upswept tip it offers plenty of useful cutting edge. On a knife this small creating a solid grip is tough. Rick designed the grip so that your hand comes forward past the pivot point enabling a full three-finger grip on this smaller knife. The handle is faux G-10 textured to enhance grip even more; the blade has a stonewashed finish that looks great and hides scratches.

The secure locking liner features cutout embellishments revealed by the design of the handle scale. This design also makes it easier to open this manual-opening blade and easier to unlock the liner lock to close it. The large lanyard hole makes attaching the Cinder to your key chain or pack simple.

And you might have noticed the bottle opener built into the back end. Yeah we thought you did. It?s plenty sturdy and ready to go to work when you are.

products.name: Kershaw Camp 10 Fixed Machete Knife 10" Recurve Blade Tan and Black
products.description:
The popular Kershaw Camp 10 machete has been widely praised for both value and durability. The black-and-tan color scheme was inspired by a Camp 10 that was put to work and got all dusty in the process. Turns out it looked pretty good. Cut slash hack split scrape—just about any task you ask of it the Camp 10 Tan can handle. From clearing brush to making kindling the Camp 10 Tan is the ideal outdoor and survival tool. 

  • 10-inch blade provides hacking power in a perfect size
  • Full-tang construction; 65Mn steel a durable carbon steel; black powdercoat for added blade protection
  • Glass-filled nylon handle with rubberized overmold offers secure grip
  • Includes glass-filled nylon sheath with gear straps and belt loop

products.description:
The Camp 5 is a big blade-forward Bowie-style knife that’s ready for your next adventure. This fixed-blade full-tang knife is ideal for survival camping bushcrafting or just about any outdoor activity. Its D2 blade steel is a great choice for a hard-use knife like this. This high-carbon high-chromium tool steel offers good edge retention and hardness while being more corrosion resistant than other high-carbon steels. A machined texture on the glass-filled nylon handle scales provides a secure grip. Kershaw put a lot of thought into the molded sheath too.   • D2 blade steel for edge retention hardness and corrosion resistance

products.description:
The lightweight Kershaw Reverb is ideal for backpacking camping hiking and other outdoor activities. With its lightweight design and no flipper or thumb stud to catch on anything the Reverb is ready to go with you on your next outdoor adventure. The built-in carabiner clip makes it easy to clip to backpack or harness.

The Reverb is a manual opening knife but can be opened one-handed thanks to the large machined recess in the blade. Just use your thumb to push outward on the recess and rotate the blade into place—with no protruding thumb stud or flipper in the way.

The Reverb offers a reliable blade of 8Cr13MoV that takes and holds its Kershaw-sharp edge for a long time. Its modified drop-point blade shape is perfect for just about any task you’ll encounter. Grey PVD coating on the grinds provides additional protection against the elements. A satin finish on the blade flats and on part of the back handle adds visual interest. The front handle scale is light-yet-strong G-10 with a carbon fiber overlay and contoured for a solid grip.

For safe use the Reverb has a secure frame lock to lock the blade open during use. It also features a built-in carabiner clip that makes it easy to attach to a backpack or harness for easy access. Alternatively you can pocket-carry the Reverb. It’s equipped with a special deep-carry pocketclip that allows for extra-deep carry so that even in an active outdoor situation it will stay securely down in your pocket.

  • Carabiner clip
  • Manual opening
  • Frame lock
  • Single-position extra-deep-carry pocketclip (right tip-up)

products.name: Kershaw Narrow Fillet Knife - 9-1/2" Length (Clamshell)
products.description:
The Kershaw 9.5-inch fillet's blade is the right size for salmon pike steelhead and most larger fish. Because of the greater girth of these fish and the extra surface area you?ll need to cut through you'll appreciate having a longer blade.

The blade is razor-sharp 420J2 stainless steel for excellent corrosion resistance - always important for use in a wet environment. The steel is also quite tough and easy to re-sharpen. What?s more it offers just the right amount of ?flex? to make filleting easier and to preserve the delicate flesh and flavor of the fish.

The handle is glass-filled nylon for durability and has a rubberized overmold with our exclusive K-Texture grip. The K-Texture pattern ensures you always have a secure hold - even in slippery conditions. For easy storage the 9.5-inch Fillet with K-Texture includes a blade protector.

products.name: Kershaw Starter Folding Knife 3-2/5" Drop Point Blade Blackwash
products.description:
The BlackWash finish gives it a rough-and-tumble look yet the finish isn’t just for looks. The coating provides an extra measure of protection for the metal and the BlackWash helps hide any additional scratches you put on the knife during normal use.

The Starter is equipped with SpeedSafe assisted opening for fast and easy one-handed opening. It opens neatly with the built-in flipper or thumbstud. A liner lock safely secures the blade open during use and then closes easily for storage or carry. The all-steel design really shows off the BlackWash finish.

The Starter includes our deep-carry pocketclip so the knife rides comfortably low in the pocket for discreet carry.

products.name: Kershaw Grinder Folding Knife 3-1/4" Clip Point Blade Black
products.description:
The Kershaw Grinder is designed to be put to work.

To that end the Grinder offers a blade with a slightly curved belly for all-purpose cutting and slicing. A clipped tanto-inspired tip offers excellent piercing capabilities too. If you need to bear down on the back of the blade during a particularly tough cutting job the concave spine with heavy jimping provides additional grip security. The work-ready blade is made of 4Cr13MoV steel for solid service.

The Grinder is always ready to go to work quickly thanks to the Kershaw SpeedSafe assisted opening and convenient built-in flipper. A secure liner lock keeps the blade securely open during work until the user releases it. The glass-filled nylon handle is ergonomically contoured to fit the hand securely and grooved to offer an extra-secure grip. The deep-carry pocket clip is easily reversible for tip-down right- or left-handed carry.

products.name: Kershaw Cathode Folding Knife 2-1/4" American Tanto Blade Silver
products.description:
In a battery the cathode attracts the positive charge. One look at Kershaw’s new Cathode tanto and we predict you’ll have a very positive attraction indeed.

The Cathode isn’t ultra fancy just ultra functional. The 2.25 inch tanto blade is great for slicing and piercing. A top grind adds a touch of style while heavy jimping on the spine ensures a secure grip - especially when you need to choke up on the blade for detail work. The blade opens with a flipper and our SpeedSafe assisted opening so one-handed opening is a breeze. And since it’s a flipper knife it’s perfect for left or right-handed users.

The handle is stainless steel hot-stamped with a repeating pattern that’s not only looks good but also enhances grip. The Cathode locks up securely during use thanks to the solid frame lock. Black hardware including a backspacer with additional jimping and a reversible pocketclip sets off the Cathode’s all-steel good looks.

products.description:
The Lightyear is an entry in the Kershaw Starter Series designed as a slim effective knife at an attractive price. The first thing users will notice about the Lightyear is its horn-like profile. products.name: Kershaw Cryo Folding Knife 2-3/4" Drop Point Blade Matte Grey
products.description:
If you’ve been craving a Rick Hinderer knife but couldn’t quite part with the bucks your last excuse has just disappeared. The Cryo is the result of collaboration between Rick Hinderer and the design and production engineers at Kershaw. And we’re sure it will satisfy both your Hinderer craving and the demands of your wallet.

A classic Rick Hinderer design the Cryo is built of pure stainless steel coated with matte grey titanium carbo-nitride for a no-fuss look that lets the design shine through. Like all Rick’s knives the Cryo benefits from Rick’s real world experience as a fire fighter and EMT. It’s designed to be a sturdy knife that’s still aesthetically pleasing and feels good in the hand.

For secure blade lock up the Cryo offers a tough frame lock with lockbar stabilization. The Cryo also features Kershaw’s SpeedSafe assisted opening for fast and easy one-handed opening. Access it with either the built-in flipper or the thumbstud.

Slightly smaller than some Hinderer pocketknives the Cryo is a superb knife for every day carry. EDC this guy for a while and we think you’ll soon appreciate its virtues. You get the tactical hard-use looks you’re looking for a Hinderer design and SpeedSafe opening in this amazingly affordable Kershaw that’s destined to be the Hinderer for the rest of us.

This Kershaw spring assisted knife features a 2-3/4" plain drop point blade made from 8Cr13MoV steel.

8Cr13MoV steel and the MoV (or Cr) series of steels originate from China and are equivalent to AUS-8 but containing slightly higher carbon content. You typically get great value for money with this steel and Kershaw have perfected the heat treatment process to bring out its best. 8Cr13MoV means that this knife's steel contains approximately .8% carbon and 13% Chromium. 8Cr13MoV is a very capable steel with no evident weaknesses. Leading knife makers compare it to AUS-8. It retains its edge well but is not as abrasion resistant as VG-10 or S30V. Edge stability is good which means the edge can be thinned well. We've found that this steel is among the least complicated to hone. Kershaw's 8Cr13MoV steel is usually hardened to HRC 58-60.

Drop point blades are a style of knife blade that slopes on the spine of the blade from the handle of the knife to the tip of the blade. This allows the spine of the blade (where the blade is thicker and accordingly stronger) to continue forward to the tip of the blade. This way the point is also aligned with the center axis of the knife removing any pitch momentum when stabbing.

The curve on the top of a drop-point blade is always convex which is what distinguishes it from a clip point blade. The drop point is a common design for hunting.

This spring assisted knife has a 410/Titanium Carbo-Nitride handle.

products.name: Kershaw Blur Semi Serrated Folding Knife 3-2/5" Drop Point Blade Black
products.description:
It’s equipped with a big slightly recurved blade that’s ideal for multitasking. The blade shape offers both excellent slicing and piercing capabilities and the high-performance Sandvik 14C28N stainless blade steel offers corrosion resistance and hardness. The black Blur has a DLC (Diamond-Like Carbon) coated blade for extra corrosion resistance and enhanced looks. This Blur's partially serrated blade provides additional cutting power for making short work of rope cord and other fibrous materials.

As you might expect the black Blur has black handles with Trac-Tec grip-tape handle inserts for an extremely solid grip. The handle itself is durable 6061-T6 anodized aluminum sometimes described as “aircraft aluminum” since it is a common material used for aircraft fittings. But the main point is that it’s lightweight extremely durable and—when anodized—accepts a dye so we can create colored handles that are scratch resistant and extra tough.

For easy one-handed opening the Blur is equipped with SpeedSafe assisted opening. A short push on the thumbstud overcomes the resistance built into the torsion bar in the SpeedSafe mechanism. The SpeedSafe takes over and the blade moves out of the handle quickly and easily. One-handed opening is easy with SpeedSafe. The pocketclip is reversible for your choice of tip-up or tip-down carry. There’s even a pre-drilled lanyard hole.
 

  • Made in the USA
  • SpeedSafe assisted opening
  • Locking liner
  • Thumbstud
  • Reversible (tip-up/tip-down) pocketclip
  • Steel: Sandvik 14C28N DLC coating
  • Handle: 6061-T6 anodized aluminum Trac-Tec inserts
  • Blade length: 3.4 in. (8.6 cm)
  • Closed length: 4.5 in. (11.4 cm)
  • Overall length: 7.9 in. (20 cm)
  • Weight: 3.9 oz. (110.6 g)

products.description:
The Dividend is more striking than ever with its new Composite Blade and machined and anodized aluminum handle. Kershaw’s proprietary Composite Blade Technology joins two steels in one blade. In this case CPM D2 and Bohler N690. We put the Bohler N690 on the blade upper to take advantage of its corrosion resistance and exceptional hardness. We put the D2 on the cutting edge to take advantage of its wear resistance toughness and excellent edge retention. Then we permanently joined them in a “toothlike” pattern for warbird-like style.

The Oso Sweet is indeed one sweet pocketknife. It features a classic drop-point blade that gives you maximum workaday utility at the same time it has plenty of style and features that will get it—and you—noticed. The Oso Sweet is one of our most popular knives. Once you get your hands on one and start using it it will be pretty popular with you too.

  • A do-it-all pocketknife that’s easy to EDC
  • Quality 8Cr13MoV blade steel; attractive machine satin finish
  • Durable glass-filled nylon handle with unique “scale” pattern for enhanced grip
  • Easy quick opening with Kershaw's assisted opening

products.name: Kershaw Kuro Folding Knife 3-1/10" Partially Serrated American Tanto Blade Black
products.description:
The Kuro’s blade is an Americanized tanto with partial serration and a drop point for strong piercing. The edge provides good slashing capability while the partial blade serration offers versatility for cutting fibrous materials with ease. For speedy one-handed opening the Kuro has Kershaw's assisted opening accessed with the built-in flipper. The ambidextrous flipper works perfectly for both lefties and righties. The handle scales are glass-filled nylon for durability and dimensional stability even in temperature extremes. The eye-catching pattern on the scales offers additional grip traction and looks like nothing else.

  • The Kuro offers standout looks—and standout function
  • 8Cr13MoV blade steel offers edge-holding capability strength and hardness; black-oxide coating adds blade protection
  • Lightweight strong glass-filled nylon handle
  • Fast easy opening with Kershaw's assisted opening and flipper
  • 3-position pocketclip

products.name: Kershaw Lonerock RBK 2 Folding Knife 2-4/5" Drop Point Blade Tan and Black
products.description:
The manual opening LoneRock RBK 2 is an upgraded version of Kershaw’s skinning and caping knife. Like the original it includes replaceable surgical-precision blades. Instead of having to stop and sharpen when a knife gets dull in the middle of skinning just snap in a new blade and keep working. A liftable liner allows users to remove and replace blades safely and easily with a non-slip grip. The RBK 2 also features a revamped handle for greater ergonomics and longer work sessions. It comes with 15 blades and a “buddy” handle. This slim extra handle holds an RBK 2 blade so that both you and your buddy can take on the skinning task—to get the job done quicker.

  • Easy-to-use skinning and caping knife; new ergonomic olive handle
  • #60A scalpel blades; safely remove with new easy-to-use liner
  • Opens manually
  • Includes 15 replacement blades extra “buddy” handle and sheath to contain it all

products.name: Kershaw Select Fire Folding Knife 3-2/5" Drop Point Blade Black
products.description:
Most multi-tools include a plethora of “tools” many of which are not actually very useful. Even worse in many of these tools the all-important knife blade is an afterthought—and barely useful at all. Not the Select Fire. The Select Fire was built to be a knife-focused multi-tool. There’s a big task-ready blade plus a 4-piece bit set and bit driver.

  • 4-piece bit set ruler plus full-sized blade
  • 8Cr13MoV quality blade steel bead-blasted finish gives blade a matte look
  • Sturdy glass-filled nylon handle with swing out bit carrier; choose from two flat head two Phillips bits
  • Reversible pocketclip for left-handed or right-handed carry
