products.name: Kershaw Mini Iridium Folding Knife 3" Spear Point Blade Black
products.description:
We made the popular Iridium even easier to carry with an ultra-stealthy mini version complete with an all-black look. That includes a black-anodized handle and a backspacer with a lanyard hole. Activate with the thumb stud and experience buttery smooth deployment with KVT ball bearings. Ultra-secure DuraLock technology locks the blade in place. The D2 spear point blade is ideal for everyday cutting tasks. When your work is done slide the lock back to safely close the Mini Iridium and carry it with a reversible deep-carry pocket clip. Black never goes out of style; that’s why this Mini Iridium is a winner.

  • Mini-size everyday carry; stylish and stealthy all-black design
  • DuraLock secures the blade open using a solid steel crossbar; pull the ambidextrous lock back to safely close the knife
  • D2 high-carbon tool steel is highly wear resistant tough offers excellent edge retention; black-oxide coating offers extra blade protection
  • Opens easily with KVT ball-bearing system and thumb studs
  • Deep-carry pocketclip is easily reversible for left/right carry; black anodized backspacer and lanyard hole

products.name: Kershaw Analyst Folding Knife 3-1/4" Partially Serrated Tanto Blade Black
products.description:
One look at the Analyst reveals a tough Kershaw with plenty of work-ready features. Its tanto combo edge allows for versatile cutting ability. A serrated edge saws through rope and fabrics while the tanto point excels at piercing. The 3.25-inch blade can be easily opened with Kershaw's assisted opening. Glass-filled nylon texturing and spine jimping provide an extra-secure grip. A BlackWash blade finish hides use scratches after a hard day of work. Finally the deep-carry pocketclip can be swapped to four positions further enhancing its versatility. After closer examination the Analyst proves to be a dependable work tool for many cutting tasks.

  • Tactical work knife featuring a combo edge and tanto blade shape
  • 8Cr13MoV blade steel offers edge-holding capability strength and hardness; BlackWash™ finish helps hide use scratches
  • Glass-filled nylon texturing provides grip during use; liner lock secures the blade open
  • Opens quickly and easily with Kershaw's assisted opening and built-in flipper
  • Included lanyard hole; deep-carry pocketclip is adjustable to four positions

products.name: Kershaw Brace Neck Knife 2" Fixed Drop Point Blade
products.description:
Many appreciate the convenience of small neck knives but actual utility is sometimes overlooked. That’s where the Brace comes in. Despite its small profile the fixed blade has many features that enhance grip including a curved handle guard design jimping and a front handle cutout for an alternate thumb grip. These grippy additions let users get the most out its 2-inch blade. During travel secure the knife in a polypropylene neck sheath. Its dual-retention system keeps the Kershaw secure. With the sheath the full-tang knife only weighs 1.6 ounces. The Brace is easy to carry but it also packs a punch as a utilitarian winner.

  • A full-tang neck knife for travel and utility
  • 8Cr13MoV blade steel offers edge-holding capability strength and hardness; stonewashed finish helps hide use scratches
  • Steel handle is contoured for grip and comfort removeable glass-filled nylon overlay
  • Molded sheath features dual-retention system for secure carrying; knife can be sheathed whether its flipped left or right

products.name: Kershaw Endgame Folding Knife 3-1/4" Spear Point Blade Bronze Silver
products.description:
For a combination of high-quality materials intricate design elements and practical usability step into the Kershaw Endgame. After opening the knife with KVT ball bearings take control of the 3.25-inch drop point blade and use its high-retention D2 tool steel. The handle is contoured for comfortable finger placement and a deep-carry pocketclip is reversible for convenient carry. Unique design elements help the Endgame stand out including a series of overlays. Some are made of glass filled nylon and others coated with bronze PVD. This creates an interesting multi-layered appearance. Being jam-packed with features the Endgame is the total package for any collection.

  • Modern design; sharp performance
  • D2 high-carbon tool steel is highly wear resistant tough offers excellent edge retention; stonewashed finish helps hide use scratches
  • Steel handle includes bronze PVD-coated and glass-filled nylon overlays; frame lock secures the blade open
  • Opens easily with KVT ball-bearing system and a flipper
  • Decorative pivot cap; deep-carry pocketclip is easily reversible for left/right carry

products.name: Kershaw Ultra Tek Knife Sharpener
products.description:
The Ultra-Tek Blade Sharpener is the convenient way to keep your Kershaw sharp. The Ultra-Tek is a compact sharpening steel that lets you quickly and easily touch up the edge on your Kershaw anywhere anytime. The Ultra-Tek handle is made of 6060-T6 anodized aircraft aluminum.

Stored inside the handle is a 600-grit diamond-coated oval shaft. This is the perfect grit for restoring an edge that is in generally good shape but is just dull. Simply unscrew the shaft from the handle interior turn it around and screw it on to the other end of the handle. Now the Ultra-Tek is a comfortable 9-in. length ideal for both sharpening and realigning the edge of your Kershaw blade. To sharpen hold the blade edge against the diamond-coated shaft at about a 20-degree angle and swipe the blade from heel to tip along the sharpening shaft. Do this an even number of times on both sides of the blade. Soon your blade will be restored to it's Kershaw shaving sharp edge. It's a good idea to keep the Ultra-Tek close at hand so you can touch up the blade from time to time. If you don't let it get terribly dull it will take no time at all to maintain your edge.

The Ultra-Tek requires no water or oil. It's lightweight and easy to use. And it stores compactly making it easy to take with you.
 

  • Steel: 600-grit diamond-coated oval shaft
  • Handle: 6061-T6 anodized aluminum
  • Sharpening steel length: 4 in. (10.1 cm)
  • Overall Length: 9 in. (22.9 cm)
  • Stored length: 5 in. (12.7 cm)
  • Weight: 2.1 oz. (59.5 g)

products.name: Kershaw Static Knife with Flipper Open / Stainless Steel Handle - 2-4/5" Blade
products.description:
With its cleaver-shaped blade the Kershaw Static excels at cutting slicing and chopping. The blade is sturdy just under three inches long and features a slightly curved belly for enhanced versatility. The cleaver-style tip provides good piercing capabilities while retaining the characteristic cleaver shape.

8Cr13MoV blade steel to take and hold a work-worthy edge no matter the demands of the task. The Static opens one-handed with KVT ball-bearings and a flipper. A sturdy frame lock keeps the blade secure while you work.

The Static?s stainless steel handle features angled machining that provides traction for a solid grip. The gray PVD coating is hard and wear resistant. All this makes the Static is an ideal work and utility knife that's also easy to EDC. It folds down to a compact 3.8 inches and slides neatly into your pocket. The deep-carry pocketclip is left/right reversible and allows the knife to ride comfortably low in your pocket.

  • KVT ball-bearing opening
  • Flipper
  • Frame lock
  • Reversible deep-carry pocketclip (right/left tip-up)
  • Steel: 8Cr13MoV satin finish

products.name: Kershaw Bracket Folding Knife 3-2/5" Cleaver Blade Black
products.description:
The Bracket is an XL version of the original Static cleaver. But rather than a simple size change it has some fresh additions as well. A new glass-filled nylon front handle scale is plenty grippy and its steel pivot overlay adds visual interest. Functionally the Bracket opens easily with Kershaw's assisted opening. A large choil allows users to enhance their grip. The deep-carry pocketclip is reversible for right or left carry and the handle also includes a new lanyard hole. Even with its changes the knife weight is just as balanced the Static. Yet the Bracket does something different while remaining a practical and fun cleaver for the collection.

  • Cleaver-style blade for top cutting performance; plus-size version of the Static
  • 8Cr13MoV blade takes a sharp edge and is easy to re-sharpen when needed; stonewashed finish helps hide use scratches
  • Textured glass-filled nylon front handle includes steel pivot overlay; stainless steel back
  • Opens quickly and easily with Kershaw's assisted opening and built-in flipper
  • Included lanyard hole; deep-carry pocketclip is easily reversible for left/right carry

products.name: Kershaw Iredale Folding Pocketknife 2 3/5" Clip Point Blade Black
products.description:
Named after the Peter Iredale shipwreck in Astoria Oregon the Iredale pays respect to history while also pushing forward with a fresh design. Featuring a non-locking slipjoint mechanism the Iredale includes a clip point blade and two sheepsfoot blades. Any of them can be used for everyday tasks depending on the size and type of job. The polished micarta handle adds style and strength to the knife along with steel bolsters and brass liners. It’s traditional yes but this three-bladed Kershaw stands out in the modern era with plenty of character.

  • Unique non-locking slipjoint style; includes clip point and two sheepsfoot blades
  • Polished canvas micarta handle; steel bolsters with brass liners
  • 7Cr17MoV stainless steel blades offer good edge retention toughness and wear resistance; satin polished for a traditional look
  • Opens manually with nail nick
  • Blade lengths: 2.6" 2.2" 1.6"

products.name: Kershaw Lucha Folding Knife 4-3/5" Drop Point Blade Silver
products.description:
Do you flip? Do you want to flip? Then the Kershaw Lucha is for you. This is a high-quality butterfly knife that’s made in the USA. Next level materials include a 14C28N stainless steel blade and all-steel handle. Next level performance comes from Kershaw’s meticulous design. For instance the blade tapers so that the top has more weight to pendulum around smoothly. The Lucha features dual KVT ball-bearing pivots for extra-easy operation. The handle has a rounded bevel so it rolls effortlessly in the hand. Even the latch is rounded so it never catches as you flip. The latch also features a positive stop so it never contacts the blade. The full-sized Lucha was designed with feedback from real flippers. This light fast butterfly knife will jump fly and spin in your hands.

  • Made-in-the-USA butterfly knife designed with flippers in mind
  • 14C28N stainless steel blade; increased nitrogen in the formula provides excellent corrosion resistance and hardenability
  • Rounded handle bevels let the Lucha roll smoothly in the hand
  • Dual KVT ball-bearing pivots for ultra-smooth flipping
  • Perfect size weight and design for flipping

The Lucha is sold only through authorized Kershaw dealers; the webpage is for information only. Comply with all local state and federal regulations regarding the purchase possession and transportation of knives.

products.name: Keshaw Emerson CQC-6K D2 Folding EDC Kife with Wave Shaped Opening Feature
products.description:
This Kershaw Emerson knife now comes with D2 blade steel. D2 a high-carbon highchromium tool steel is a knifemaker favorite and offers good edge retentionand hardness. For a secure grip the knife has a G10 front scale and steel back. A sturdy frame lock secures the blade open during use. And of course the knife also features the patented Emerson Wave Shaped Feature for fast and easy opening.

This Kershaw?Emerson now comes with D2 blade steel. D2 a high-carbon high-chromium tool steel is a knifemaker favorite and offers good edge retention and hardness as well as being more corrosion resistant that other high-carbon steels.

The Kershaw Emerson CQC-6K D2 is a manual opener using either the thumb disk or the patented Emerson Wave Shaped Feature. This opening feature enables the knife to be opened as it is removed from the pocket. By the time the knife has been fully withdrawn from the pocket the blade is deployed and ready for use. A small wave-shaped tab on the top of the blade is built to catch on the pocket seam opening the knife as it comes out of the pocket. This instant-open feature is a favorite among military rescue and law enforcement knife users.

  • Designed by Emerson built by Kershaw
  • Manual opening
  • Thumb disk; Emerson Wave Shaped Feature
  • Frame lock
  • Reversible pocketclip (left/right tip-up)
  • Lanyard hole
  • Steel: D2 stonewashed & satin finish
  • Handle: G10 front; 410 stainless steel back bead-blasted finish
  • Blade Length: 3.25 in. (8.3 cm)
  • Closed Length: 4.5 in. (11.4 cm)
  • Overall Length: 7.75 in. (19.7 cm)
  • Weight: 5.1 oz. (144.6 g)

The Launch 8 has the symmetrical lines of a stiletto is very lightweight—only 2.4 ounces—and easy-to-carry. products.name: Kershaw Barricade Rescue Folding Knife 3-1/2" Drop Point Blade Orange with Carbide Glassbreaker Tip and Seatbelt Cutter
products.description:
The Kershaw Barricade is a value-priced rescue knife with standout features & standout color.

A bulwark against unpreparedness the Barricade has all the key features needed in an emergency knife all wrapped up in a bright orange “see me” package. A carbide glassbreaker is built into the butt end. The sculpted glass-filled nylon handle offers a secure grip whether in glass-striking position or when using the blade. If needed to free a trapped victim the built-in cord cutter will zip through seat belts and cord quickly and easily.

The blade steel is 8Cr13MoV which can take and hold a sharp edge yet resharpens easily. Kershaw’s skilled heat treatment brings out the best in this top-value steel. The blade is black-oxide coated to add an extra measure of protection from the elements. A secure liner lock keeps the blade locked safely open during use then closes easily when your tasks are done.

The modified clip-point blade opens one-handed with SpeedSafe assisted opening and the flipper. For convenient carry it also features a deep-carry pocketclip that enables the knife to ride securely low in your pocket.

products.name: Kershaw Shuffle Folding Steel Knife 2-1/4" Blade Black Handle
products.description:
The Shuffle is a compact versatile & tough multi-function tool. You'll like its compact size and discovering how useful that stubby little blade really is. You'll also like how nicely the finger contours fit your hand and how our K-Texture handle provides an extra secure grip.

The Shuffle has some additional tricks up its sleeve too. It has a flathead screwdriver at the butt of the knife which doubles as a lanyard attachment and a handy bottlecap lifter built into the back of the knife.

The blade is made of made of a steel known for toughness and durability. The K-Texture handle - composed of a repeating pattern of the Kershaw logo "k" - is exclusive to Kershaw and enhances grip. A liner lock secures the Shuffle's blade open in use but closes easily when its tasks are done.

As a utility knife a work knife or just a great multi-function pocketknife the Shuffle is the right choice. And if you want an eye-catching look in a new knife with the Shuffle "snow" you can't go wrong.

This Kershaw folding knife features a 2-1/4" plain drop point blade made from 8Cr13MoV steel.

8Cr13MoV steel and the MoV (or Cr) series of steels come from China and are comparable to AUS-8 but containing slightly higher carbon content. You routinely get great value for money with this steel and Kershaw have perfected the heat treatment process to bring out its best. 8Cr13MoV means that this knife's steel contains roughly .8% carbon and 13% Chromium. 8Cr13MoV is a very capable steel with no real weaknesses. Top knife makers compare it to AUS-8. It maintains its edge well but is not as abrasion resistant as VG-10 or S30V. Edge stability is good which means the edge can be thinned well. We've found that this steel is among the easiest to hone. Kershaw's 8Cr13MoV steel is usually hardened to HRC 58-60.

Drop point blades are a style of knife blade that angles on the spine of the blade from the handle of the knife to the tip of the blade. This allows the spine of the blade (where the blade is thicker and thus stronger) to continue forward to the tip of the blade. This way the point is also aligned with the center axis of the knife canceling any pitch momentum when stabbing.

The curve on the top of a drop-point blade is always convex which is what differentiates it from a clip point blade. The drop point is a standard design for hunting.

This folding knife has a Glass-filled Nylon/K-Texture Grip handle with a black finish.

products.name: Kershaw TX-TOOL Multi-Tool
products.description:
Switching a pocketclip tightening a screw or adjusting the pivot tension - now Kershaw owners have the right tool for every adjustment: the new TX-Tool.

The TX-Tool is our new and improved T-Tool. It includes five key bits for adjusting all your Kershaws: T-6 T-8 and T-10 for most Kershaws plus the slotted and Phillips screwdriver bits for the Kershaw–Emersons.

A magnetic bit driver tip makes it easy to change bits. Even better all bits store conveniently inside the TX-Tool's handle. A pocketclip with a cutout Kershaw logo “K” makes it easy to carry the TX-Tool wherever you go.

Note: the TX-Tool is not covered by the Kershaw Limited Lifetime Warranty.

products.name: Ka-Bar Ka-Bar USMC Fixed Knife 7" Clip Point Blade Brown with Sheath
products.description:
The Ka-Bar K1 USMC Full Size Fighting Knife (w/Sheath) is ranked as the most famous knife worldwide. However the company has recently made upgrades making it better than ever. Overall the knife measures 11 7/8 inches long while the blade is 7 inches in length.

This knife also boasts a 20-degree angled edge and is made from strong and durable stainless steel. The handle is ground flat and wrapped in leather. Included in the price of this American-made product is a sheath made from glass-filled nylon with everything guaranteed by the company.

products.name: Ka-Bar Spork/Knife Black
products.description: The KA-BAR Spork which is made from food and water approved Grilamid is equipped with a fork/spoon combo and has a 2.5" plastic serrated knife in the handle.  The knife is accessed by pulling the spork in opposite directions from each extreme end. **Hint--avoid gripping the flat panel area in the middle of the Spork--this is actually part of its lock. products.name: TacMed Solutions Field Trauma Kit Level 1
products.description:
The Field Trauma Kit (FTK) is your essential kit for immediate trauma response. Developed by Special Operations Forces Medics this compact first-aid kit is equipped to handle serious injuries. Each component has stood the test of time in the field ensuring reliability when you need it most.

Its compact design allows it to easily fit into your gear setup making it accessible for emergency situations. Secured in a waterproof pouch it goes wherever you go ensuring preparedness for heavy bleeding and penetrating chest trauma scenarios.

Specs: 8"H x 6.75"W x 3.5"D 0.5lbs

  • TacMed Compact Trauma Bandage
  • 1x Chest Seal
  • 1x Esmark Bandage
  • 1x Compressed Gauze
  • 1x CPR Face Shield
  • 1x 1PR Nitrile Gloves

products.name: Stealth Operator TacMed Solutions SOF Tourniquet
products.description:
The SOF Tourniquet by TacMed Solutions sets the benchmark for pre-hospital tourniquets. Designed for rapid one-handed and two-handed applications the SOF Tourniquet’s reinforced low-stretch polyester pressure band easily slides over an arm or a leg. Its durable buckle quickly unhooks and re-hooks allowing access to confined spaces and trapped limbs.

A patented indicator wedge is stitched beneath the windlass to visually confirm when all slack is removed ensuring an effective application. It features a patented aircraft grade aluminum windlass rod with a textured grip for consistent twisting. The windlass secures into a Tri-Ring Lock and Tourniquet Retention Assistance Clip (TRAC). 

Features:

  • The preferred tourniquet of elite military forces and first responders world-wide
  • The tourniquet of choice by 7/10 of the USA’s largest police departments
  • Meets new ANSI standards: 100%
  • JEMS Hot Product from EMS Today 2021
  • Exclusive tourniquet of the American Red Cross
  • 5” machined aircraft grade aluminum windlass rod
  • 1.5” reinforced low-stretch polyester strap
  • Detachable UV-resistant high-strength composite friction-lock buckle
  • Tri-Ring Lock and Tourniquet Retention Assistance Clip for windlass securement
  • Low-profile with no catch points when folded and staged
  • Easy one-handed application

The SOF Tourniquet was designed by Special Forces medics and has been rigorously tested on and off the battlefield. It is the preferred tourniquet for elite military forces and emergency first responders worldwide.

products.name: Lee Chamfer Tool
products.description:
The Lee Chamfer Tool is just the tool you need to quickly and easily remove the burrs that are made when trimming cartridge cases. A single turn is all you need with the Lee Chamfer Tool to chamfer and deburr both the inside and outside necks of trimmed cartridge cases.

The Lee Chamfer Tool was made from hardened steel and designed in a unique way to cut quickly and easily without any chatter. This tool makes quick work of chamfer and deburring

products.name: Lee Case Trimmer and Lock Stud
products.description:
The Lee Case Trimmer and Lock Stud was specifically designed for use with Lee case length shellholders and gauges. This trimmer and lock stud was manufactured from hardened steel to ensure easy and accurate case trimming ability that meets SAMMI specifications.

Not only does the Lee Case Trimmer and Lock Stud ensure accurate case trimming each and every time but the shaft ensures that the tool can be turned either by hand or used with an electric drill. This cutter and lock stud works for all calibers so you do not need to waste money buying multiple tools or adapters.

products.name: Lee Case Length Gage and Shell Holder .22 Hornet
products.description:
The Lee Case Length Gauge and Shell Holder comes in a wide variety of sizes to accommodate all of the most popular cartridge calibers. This set of tools is made from hardened steel to ensure a lifetime of durable performance and is precision-crafted to tight SAAMI specifications.

The Lee Case Length Gauge gives you a fast and accurate way to trim your brass cases while also squaring the mouths. The shell holder is used to hold the case firmly in place during this operation and while using your Lee Case Trimmer Cutter. These tools help to ensure the maximum level of accuracy in trimming and squaring your brass cases.

The Lee Case Length Gauge and Shell Holder comes in a wide variety of sizes to accommodate all of the most popular cartridge calibers. This set of tools is made from hardened steel to ensure a lifetime of durable performance and is precision-crafted to tight SAAMI specifications.

The Lee Case Length Gauge gives you a fast and accurate way to trim your brass cases while also squaring the mouths. The shell holder is used to hold the case firmly in place during this operation and while using your Lee Case Trimmer Cutter. These tools help to ensure the maximum level of accuracy in trimming and squaring your brass cases.

products.name: Lee Trimmer Cutter With Ball Grip - No Lock Stud
products.description:
The Lee Cutter with Ball Grip (No Lock Stud) works with all caliber sizes so you do not need to waste money buying multiple tools or adapters. This cutter was designed to quickly and easily trim your cartridge cases after they have been stretched from being loaded multiple times.

Not only is the Lee Cutter with Ball Grip versatile enough for use with multiple calibers but it can also be turned either by hand or used with an electric drill. This handy tool eliminates the danger of long cases and also squares the case mouth for more accurate seating and exiting of the bullet.

products.name: Lee Large Cutter and Lock Stud
products.description:
The Lee Large Cutter with Lock Stud is the tool you need for .500 Smith and Wesson .480 Ruger and .50 BMG cases. This tool can also be used with any case diameter smaller than .475. Simply put this Large Cutter with Lock Stud from Lee is both highly versatile and reliable.

In addition to quickly and easily trimming your cartridge casing the Large Cutter with Lock Stud from Lee can be turned either by hand or with an electric drill to trim chamfer and polish your cartridge cases all with one tool.

products.name: Lee Deluxe Quick Trim Case Trimmer
products.description: The Deluxe Quick Trim Case Trimmer quickly and precisely trims your brass to the correct length at the same time it chamfers the inside and outside of the case mouth. No calipers measurement or adjustment required. Simply install the appropriate quick trim die in your press and start trimming. A click adjustable stop allows trim length adjustment in .001 of an inch increments. Allows the user to shorten case to a uniform shorter length than standard reducing trimming frequency. Includes snap on chip catcher.

products.name: Lee Large 8-32 Threaded Cutter and Lock Stud
products.description: 8-32 threaded cutter adapter & lock stud for case prep stations.

products.name: Lee Ram Swage
products.description:
The Lee Ram Swage works on all single stage or turret presses that have 7/8”-14 threads in the press frame and accept universal press shell-holders.

Features spring assisted case extraction and an all steel case guide ensures cases will be positively centered on push rod.

Shell-holderless design allows you to swage any small or large primer pocket without swapping to a different size shell-holder.

Primer pocket swaging is necessary when reloading brass that have crimped primer pockets most cases used in military or non civilian applications have this crimp. Typical cases that you will encounter primer pocket crimps are 45 ACP 223(5.56mm) 30-06 308(7.62x51) 9mm Luger and special law enforcement 40 S&W.

The hardened steel swage punch is automatically extracted from the primer pocket by five 400 pound force disc springs.

Swage holder large or small installs in seconds into your press ram with no adjustments required.

Primer pocket swaging is so fast you’ll want to swage all range brass.

Nothing reduces priming problems on a progressive press more than properly swaged primer pockets. Surplus military and police department brass is a great low cost source of cases.

Complete swaging set includes: guided 7/8”-14 threaded swage push die both large and small ram swage holder assemblies.

products.name: Lee Custom Case Length Gauge .300 PRC
products.description:
Lee Case Length Gauges are a precise easy way to trim to length and square the case mouth.

Used with the Cutter and Lock Stud or Zip Trim. The first step to successfully trimming brass cases with the Lee Case Length Gauge and Shell Holder is to take the Lee Lock Stud (sold separately) and screw it into the shell holder. Next the Length Gauge needs to be screwed into the Case Trimmer Cutter (sold separately).

  • Material: Hardened Steel
  • Features: Caliber specific Shell holder and length gauge

products.name: Lee Primer Pocket Gauge Set
products.description:
Small and Large gauges to assure your brass meets the demanding SAAMI specifications for primer pocket dimensions.

Insert the “GO” plug gauge into primer pocket if it does not enter the crimp must be removed. Consider using a Lee Ram Swage or Lee APP Swage to complete this task.

If the “GO” gauge fits very loosely reverse and verify with the “NO-GO” end. If the “NO-GO” enters to the bottom of the primer pocket the primer pocket is oversized and will not reliably retain all primers.

products.name: Lee Ram Swage with FREE Primer Pocket Gauge Set
products.description:
Includes FREE Small and Large Gauges to assure any of your brass meets the demanding SAAMI specifications for primer pocket dimensions.

The Lee Ram Swage primer pocket swager works so fast that you’ll want to swage all range brass you pick-up. Works on all single stage presses with standard 7/8x14 threads in a press frame that accepts universal press shell-holders. Features spring assisted case extraction and an all steel case guide ensures cases will be positively centered on push rod.

Shell-holderless design allows you to swage any small or large primer pocket without swapping to a different size shell-holder.
 

  • FREE Primer Pocket Gauge Set
  • Works on all single stage presses with standard 7/8x14 threads
  • Shell-holderless design
  • Swage Small or Large primer pockets
  • Spring assisted case extraction
  • Steel Case Guide ensures all cases will be centered on push rod

products.name: Lee APP Swage with FREE Primer Pocket Gauge Set
products.description:
Includes FREE Small and Large Gauges to assure any of your brass meets the demanding SAAMI specifications for primer pocket dimensions.

This product is for use in the Lee APP or Deluxe APP press only. Spring assisted case extraction with integrated case guide. Easily removes the military crimp from the primer pocket while swaging the primer pocket of your brass and leaves a nice smooth entry radius for new primer.

Easy to adjust and no shell holder required - Only adjustment necessary is to change primer size.

Includes swage push die swage holder push rod small swage punch and large punch and shell holder adapter.

products.name: Lee 6 or 18 Cavity Bullet Mold Hinged Box
products.description: Lee molded storage box fits Lee 6-Cavity and 18-Cavity Bullet Molds with handles installed. Molded storage box fits your 6/18 Lee Cavity Bullet mold assembled with handles and your bullet sizing die. Box dimensions are 13.2" long x 4.7" wide x 1.8" high.

products.name: Lee Deluxe Case Conditioning Combo
products.description:
Deluxe Case Conditioning Combo includes cutter and lock stud chamfer tool primer pocket cleaner and power grip shell holder.

Features:

Cutter and lock stud

  • Lock stud locks into drill thread on the kurled shell holder to hold your brass. Thread case length gauge into cutter for trimming your brass.

Chamfer tool

  • Deburrs and chamfers the inside and outside of case neck. Also used to remove the crimp from primer pockets.

Primer pocket cleaner

  • Features a small and large end to clean out primer pockets so that primers can be fully seated for better accuracy and safety

Power grip shell holder

  • Provides a comfortable grip for holding cases during case trimming and chamfering sessions. Install into all popular priming tools that accept Auto Prime shell holders including our Lee Auto Prime and Auto Bench Prime tool (priming tool sold separately).

products.description: Designed specifically for Leupold VX-5HD/VX-6HD riflescopes this throw lever clamps on to the power selector ring. It is constructed of aircraft grade aluminum and manufactured in the U.S.A. It provides a large contact area for quick and easy magnification changes.

products.description: Designed specifically for Leupold VX-5HD/VX-6HD riflescopes this throw lever clamps on to the power selector ring. It is constructed of aircraft grade aluminum and manufactured in the U.S.A. It provides a large contact area for quick and easy magnification changes.

products.name: Leupold Tools Ring Wrench
products.description:
This ring wrench from Leupold tools is exactly what you need to install mounting rings in your firearm without risking damage to your rifle or scope. Designed to fit 30mm or 1-inch rings this ring wrench is one tool you should always keep nearby.

Like all Leupold tools and accessories the Leupold Alumina 50 Foot Parallax Adapter is designed for quality and utility. This ring wrench is made from hard injection-molded plastic to ensure durability and it is small enough to conveniently fit in your pocket or gun bag.

products.name: Leupold Lens Pen
products.description:
When it comes time to clean your scope lens reach for a Leopold Lens Pen. This lens pen is the ideal lens-cleaning tool for any and all scopes no matter what the brand.

The Leopold Lens Pen features a fully retractable natural hair brush on one end and a microfiber cleaning tip on the other end. The fact that the brush retracts when not in use means that you always have a clean brush when you need it. The microfiber cleaning tip is saturated with a state-of-the-art non-liquid cleaning compound that will remove moisture oil and fingerprints from your lens.

products.name: Leupold Scope Smith Mounting Tool
products.description: The Leupold Scope Smith Mounting Tool A Remarkably Useful tool feature one slotted screwdriver two Torx drivers and five hex head drivers. As practical in the field as on the bench the Scope Smith Mounting Tool is perfect for making windage and elevation adjustments and for installing rings and mount bases.

products.name: Leupold Torx Screw Kit
products.description:
The Leupold Torx Head Screw Kit contains 70 Torx ring screws and 80 Torx base screws a mixture of black and silver. Organized in a black polymer box these Torx screws are important to keep on hand if you have and use a Leupold scope.

All modern Leupold scopes utilize the new Torx-drive system which replaced old hex-head screws which were likely to strip. Torx screws do not strip or slip thus ensuring secure installation of your Leupold scope. Keep this Leupold Torx Head Screw Kit and your Leupold Torx Driver on hand in case you need to make any repairs or replacements.

products.name: L.E. Wilson Case Gage 223 Rem
products.description:
The Wilson Case One piece gage will check overall length to indicate the need for trimming datum to head length to assure correct headspace and to prevent over sizing. Available for most popular rimless cases.

MEASURES MIN/MAX CASE LENGTH AND MIN/MAX HEADSPACE

Note: Does not measure body diameters. This gage is intended to be used with fired cases to determine a basis for full length sizing and trimming.

Made in the USA

The Wilson Case One piece gage will check overall length to indicate the need for trimming datum to head length to assure correct headspace and to prevent over sizing. Available for most popular rimless cases.

MEASURES MIN/MAX CASE LENGTH AND MIN/MAX HEADSPACE

Note: Does not measure body diameters. This gage is intended to be used with fired cases to determine a basis for full length sizing and trimming.

Made in the USA

The Wilson Case One piece gage will check overall length to indicate the need for trimming datum to head length to assure correct headspace and to prevent over sizing. Available for most popular rimless cases.

MEASURES MIN/MAX CASE LENGTH AND MIN/MAX HEADSPACE

Note: Does not measure body diameters. This gage is intended to be used with fired cases to determine a basis for full length sizing and trimming.

products.name: L.E. Wilson  Adjustable Case Gage 300 Win Mag
products.description:
The Wilson Adjustable Case Gage allows reloaders to measure case length from the base of the cartridge to the shoulder as well as the maximum case length. This process shows the reloader if ammunition is being produced within industry specifications. 

Notes:

  • This is a two-piece adjustable cylinder-type gauge for checking fired and resized cartridge cases for cone-to-head and overall length
  • Used to compare cartridges avgainst the minimum and maximum SAAMI cartridge dimensions

products.name: Wilson Brass Case Gage .223 Rem
products.description:
One piece gage that will check overall length to indicate the need for trimming datum to head length to assure correct headspace and to prevent over sizing. Available for most popular rimless cases. The Cartridge Case Gage was designed with safety in mind and was invented by our founder Sam (L.E.) Wilson in 1935 after a fellow shooter approached him for help in solving a case-separation issue. The gage allows you to see just how much you are sizing back your shoulder on your cases. 

 

This is best done by following the steps below. 

  • Measure a case in AS-FIRED condition. Note headspace measurement 
  • Resize case on current die setting 
  • Then place back in the gage to see just how much you are sizing the shoulder back. This can be measured by using the Case Gage Depth Micrometer 
  • Finally adjust sizing die accordingly to desired shoulder set back. 

After sizing your cases there is a good chance the brass will lengthen. The gage will also check min/max case length and will point out the need for case trimming. This is an essential tool for every reloader. 

 

Note: Does not measure body diameters. This gage is intended to be used with fired cases to determine a basis for full length sizing and trimming.

products.name: L.E. Wilson Case Case Gage Depth Micrometer
products.description:
Every reloader should know exactly how much your Full Length Sizing Die is pushing back the shoulder. With the  Case Gage Depth Micrometer you can do just that.

The Depth Mic allows you to slip the micrometer perfectly over the top of the gage with your case inserted into the gage and take a measurement. Graduations of .001 comes with a Gage Block. One size works for all L.E. Wilson Gages 50 BMG Gage may not be compatible depending on if you headspace is over max dimension. We are working on a solution for this.

products.name: L.E. Wilson Case Holder (Standard) 17/222/223 Rem.
products.description:
The case holder holds the case for trimming. Cases are held by body taper NOT case head. Diameter of case and case length determines case holder size.

 The FIRED Case Holders are for Neck Sized Cases.

The case holder holds the case for trimming. Cases are held by body taper NOT case head. Diameter of case and case length determines case holder size.

 If they DO NOT make a "New Case" holder for your caliber this will be all you need and refer to these as Standard Fired Holders

 For example: Wilson only makes ONE holder for the 222/223 Remington. This will work for all Fired / New and Full Length Resized Brass

 Made in the U.S.A.

products.name: Wilson Case Length Gage .357 Mag
products.description:
One-piece non adjustable cylinder-type gage with milled surfaces on one end for checking minimum and maximum overall length of rifle and pistol cases having no shoulder.

  • Measures the Min/Max Case Length - Critical for all Straight Walled Cases
  • This Gage Does NOT Measure Body Diameters - See Pistol Max Gage or Min Dimension Gage
  • Set Case On Flat Surface Slide Gage Over Top of Case (Grooves up) Then Run Straight Edge Over Top of Gage
  • Made In the U.S.A.

products.name: L.E. Wilson Trimmer Power Adaptor
products.description:
Add Power to your Case Trimming with the Wilson Power Adapter

  • Designed to be Used with a Slow Low Power Screw Driver
  • 7/16-20 TPI - Will fit all of L.E. Wilson Brand Cutters. Including 50 Cal and TiN cutters
  • Made in the U.S.A
  • Price is for one Power Adapter

products.name: L.E. Wilson Replacement Case Trimmer Cutter
products.description:
Features:

  • The regular case trimmer cutter trims .17 to .45 caliber cases. 
  • The Trimmer Cutter is designed to trim cases to length and has been perfected over the last 70+ years to give you a flat square cut with little effort. 
  • Hardened to 60 Rockwell.
  • Trimmer Cutter = Cases up to .490 (.17 - .45)
  • Note: To be used with the Stainless Steel Case Trimmer and Stainless Micrometer Case Trimmer
  • Power Adapter compatible

products.name: L.E. Wilson Regular TiN Coated Cutter
products.description:
Features:

  • Holds Sharp Edges and Corners
  • Harder than Chrome and Carbide off Rockwell C Scale
  • Applied with a Physical Vapor Deposition (PVD) Vacuum System
  • Made In the U.S.A.

products.description:

  • New Stainless long lasting finish 
  • Coated with black oxide for a long lasting durable finish.
  • Major adjustment in the Stop Screw - 1/2 - 20 Thread with 5/8 Head on stop

  •

products.name: L.E. Wilson Deburring Tool Power Adaptor for Regular Handheld Burring Tools
products.description:
All cases should be case mouth deburred after trimming and neck turning. Use the power adaptor with your WILSON burring tool to speed up your processing time.

Get nice clean cuts on your case mouths with our super sharp case mouth deburring tool

Burring Tool and Power Screwdriver Sold Separately

Made in the USA

Power adaptor only :

  • Attaches to the Wilson Chamfer and Deburring Tool
  • Powered by a cordless screwdriver or drill (not included).
  • Power source will need to be supported to keep the trimmer level
  • Operate between 100 - 200 RPM

All cases should be case mouth deburred after trimming and neck turning. Use the power adaptor with your WILSON burring tool to speed up your processing time.

Get nice clean cuts on your case mouths with our super sharp case mouth deburring tool

Burring Tool and Power Screwdriver Sold Separately

Made in the USA

Power adaptor only :

  • Attaches to the Wilson Chamfer and Deburring Tool
  • Powered by a cordless screwdriver or drill (not included).
  • Power source will need to be supported to keep the trimmer level
  • Operate between 100 - 200 RPM

products.name: L.E. Wilson Deburring Tool .17 to .45 Caliber - Handheld
products.description:
All cases should be case mouth deburred after trimming and neck turning. Tools are double-ended with standard 45-degree flutes that debur/chamfer the inside and outside mouth of the case. They will work on cases from .17 to .45 caliber. Precision ground flutes.

Part Number: DBT-REG

 Get nice clean cuts on your case mouths with our super sharp case mouth deburring tool

 Handheld tool with optional power adaptor

 Years of use

 Precision ground flutes

 Made in the USA

products.name: Wilson Inside Neck Reamer .22 Cal
products.description:
Wilson Case Mouth Inside Neck Reamer. Use on thick case necks after multiple sizing and firings. Material build up in case necks can cause high chamber pressures and erratic shooting. Stock sizes are larger than bullet diameter and are to be used on AS-FIRED brass.

Features:

  • Reamers can be used when Forming Wildcats from a Parent case.
  • Standard reamers are sized for use on fired un-sized cases
  • Special sizes can be ground but will extend lead time please call for pricing and availability
  • Price includes one Knob Style Handle and one Inside Neck Reamer.
  • Made in the U.S.A.

products.name: Wilson Brass Minimum Dimension Gage SAAMI Chamber .223 Rem
products.description:
Ever wonder if your reloads meet min chamber dimensions? Then this is the gage for you. Made with the same tight tolerances you have come to expect from all your Wilson Tools. Best used if you are loading ammo to work in multiple gun chambers of the same caliber. We recommend using this in conjunction with the Regular Case Gage to prevent over-sizing. Gage verifies Min Chamber Dimensions and OAL for SAAMI. 

NOTE: Check with your bullet manufacturer to verify OAL this will vary depending on what grain and style bullet you are using. Min Dimensions Gages are made to SAAMI specifications for Min Chamber. SAAMI Min Chamber specs are slightly LARGER than Max Cartridge. 

The purpose of this gage is to check your reloaded rounds to see if they meet Min Chamber Specs. Therefore if your rounds do not enter the Gage then this is pointing to an issue with your reloaded round against SAAMI specifications. On the other hand if your rounds DO enter the Gage but DO NOT chamber in your gun. This points to you having a very tight chambered gun and would assume either an improperly cut reamer or a chamber that was cut below Min Chamber Dimension headspace. This does NOT mean that your round will not chamber in your specific gun's chamber. This only means the round DOES NOT meet SAAMI Min Chamber dimensions and is telling you to take another look before deciding that your round is good to fire. 

Reasons to use the Min Dimension Gage: 

  1. You want your reloaded rounds to chamber in a variety of guns 
  2. You want to check for uniformity of your rounds against SAAMI specifications 
  3. You want to pinpoint issues with your reloaded ammunition 
  4. You want a quick check to see if you are under MAX SAAMI COAL 
  5. You want to check factory ammunition you have purchased  

L.E. Wilson recommend using the Regular Case Gage for bottle necked cartridges to assist you determining how much to trim and push back your shoulder to suit your chambers headspace. Available in Select Calibers

products.name: Wilson Neck Die Stainless Steel Decapping Base
products.description: Designed to make the use of the Neck Die an easier process. Cases are pressed in with Arbor press to size the neck then flip die over on base to decap and press case out of die. Primers are collected below in empty cavity. Base works will all Neck Die Calibers.

products.name: Wilson Neck Die Stainless Steel Decapping Base
products.description: Designed to make the use of the Neck Die an easier process. Cases are pressed in with Arbor press to size the neck then flip die over on base to decap and press case out of die. Primers are collected below in empty cavity. Base works will all Neck Die Calibers.

products.name: Wilson Decapping Base - Base Only .380
products.description:
The punch and base de-caps the primer from the case while providing a stable base. Bases are case hardened for wear resistance. Available for most calibers.

  • Punch Out Primers on your Cases in a Separate Operation
  • Works Great for Military Primers
  • Many Precision Shooters Prefer to Punch Primers Out Prior to Sizing
  • To Determine the Correct Size Simply Measure your Case Head Diameter. For example a 223 Remington head measures .375" so you would need a .380 Base
  • Made in the U.S.A

products.name: Wilson Pistol Holder .357 Mag
products.description:
Pistol Holder to be Used with the Wilson Case Trimmer

  • These Hardened Holders (for fired cases only) are stocked in .38 Special .38 Super Auto .357 Magnum .44 Special .44 Magnum .40 S&W .45 Auto .45 Colt and 10 mm.  All these have practically no body taper and require a special type holder which is constructed very much like a neck sizing die.
  • Cases can’t be “bumped” in and out of these holders like most rifle cases but must be forced in with a light arbor press or mallet and must be driven or pushed out.
  • These holders are made longer than the cases to be trimmed so that cases may be forced clear in without damage to case mouth. Holders are counter-bored at mouth end for cutter clearance. 
  • Users will find the case trimmer somewhat slower on pistol cases than on rifle cases but it will produce a very uniform case length with consequent perfection in crimping.
  • Made in the U.S.A.

  • These holders are made longer than the cases to be trimmed so that cases may be forced clear in without damage to case mouth. Holders are counter-bored at mouth end for cutter clearance. 
  • Users will find the case trimmer somewhat slower on pistol cases than on rifle cases but it will produce a very uniform case length with consequent perfection in crimping.
  • Made in the U.S.A.

products.name: L.E. Wilson Pistol Max Gage 10mm Auto
products.description:
The Wilson Pistol Max (Cartridge) Gage is designed to check loaded pistol cartridges and is set to maximum SAAMI spec dimensions. This gage will measure Max Case Length Max Cartridge dimensions and Max Loaded Round Length. But more importantly it will help you to determine what is going on with your loaded ammunition. It can help to solve many issues associated with loading pistol ammunition. Such as bowing of cases during sizing oblong rounds bulge on case or crimp just to name a few. The Pistol Max Gage is a must if you are loading your own ammunition for your handguns or if you need to check purchased factory ammunition.

  •  Measures Max Case Length
  •  Measures Max Body Diameters
  •  Measures Overall Round SAAMI
  •  Made In the U.S.A.

products.name: Wilson Primer Pocket Reamer .175
products.description:
Wilson Primer Crimp Removal Tool. Used in conjunction with the Case Trimmer to remove the primer pocket crimp on military cases. The finished result is a nice rounded entry for primers.

  • Unlike some tools this tool will not distort the case head. Specify large (.210) or small (.175) when ordering. Comes with a knob style handle.
  • Used in conjunction with the Case Trimmer to remove the primer pocket crimp on military cases. The finished result is a nice rounded entry for primers
  • Precision ground flutes.
  • Price includes one Knob Style Handle and one Primer Pocket Reamer.
  • Made in the U.S.A.

products.name: Wilson Q-Type Case Holder .357 Mag/.38 Spl/.38 Super Auto
products.description:
Case Holders allow you to trim cases in your Wilson Case Trimmer. The Q-Type case holders hold the case with an easy to use cross pin. Use this type whenever possible because the regular pistol case holders require you to tap the pistol case in which is more difficult than the rifle cases because of the lack of a body taper.

  • Some Calibers May Not be Compatible with Shark Fin or Case Holder Clamp
  • For Use with the Wilson Case Trimmer
  • Designed to be Used with Straight Walled Rimmed Pistol Cases
  • Made in the U.S.A.

products.description:
Case Holders allow you to trim cases in your Wilson Case Trimmer. The Q-Type case holders hold the case with an easy to use cross pin. products.name: L.E. Wilson Reloading Tray with Bullet/Primer Cup .473" 25 Hole Black/Yellow
products.description:
Wilson Loading Trays are machined from a high quality plastic.  Machined in-house on precision equipment this tray will last for many years to come.  Makes processing groups of brass easy!  WILSON logo engraved on the end.

  • 25 Hole capacity with built in bullet/primer cup.
  • Works for cartridges with .380" .440" .473" .506" .533" case head diameter.
  • Lightweight trays good for taking with you to the range or on road trips.
  • Sort process or separate your brass.
  • Hole spacing and low profile design gives more room to get your fingers around the case.

Enhance your reloading setup with the L.E. Wilson Reloading Tray with Bullet/Primer Cup. This tray is crafted from high-quality HDPE plastic featuring excellent chemical resistance ensuring durability and longevity. The striking black and yellow color scheme adds a touch of style to your reloading bench. With 25 precisely machined holes this tray is perfect for sorting processing and separating your brass. The built-in bullet/primer cup adds convenience making it easier to handle your reloading tasks. Accommodates cartridges with options for .380" .440" and .473" case head diameter making it versatile for various reloading needs. Lightweight and portable it's ideal for taking to the range or on road trips. The low-profile design and well-spaced holes provide ample room to handle your cases with ease. Proudly made in the USA this reloading tray is a must-have for any serious reloader.

products.name: L.E. Wilson Billet Aluminum Reloading Tray .473" 55 Hole
products.description:
Wilson Loading Trays are machined from a solid block of billet aluminum.  Machined in-house on precision equipment this tray will last for many years to come.  The convenient size and stackable design make processing groups of brass easy!  WILSON logo engraved on each end.

  • Unique 55 Hole design provides flexibility in setting aside a round or two for further inspection running 50 rounds in one tray or to give you a bit more room to dispense powder.
  • Works for cartridges with a .473" diameter; this would include 22-250 Rem 220 Swift 6-250 243 Win 6 mm Rem 6 mm Creedmoor 240 Weatherby 25-06 Rem 250 Sav 260 Rem 6.5 mm Creedmoor 6.5x55 mm 270 Win 7x57 mm 7-08 Rem 280 Rem 308 Win 30-06 Sprg 8x57 mm 35 Whelen 35 Rem along with several others! 
  • Stackable lightweight trays good for taking with you to the range or on road trips.
  • Sort process or separate your brass.
  • Hole spacing and low profile design gives more room to get your fingers around the case.

The L.E. Wilson Billet Aluminum Reloading Trays are the epitome of precision and durability designed to enhance your reloading process with unmatched quality. Machined from a solid block of billet aluminum these trays boast a robust construction that ensures longevity and reliability. The clear anodized finish not only adds a sleek professional look but also provides a long-lasting protective layer. One of the standout features of these trays is their unique 55-hole design which offers incredible flexibility. Whether you need to set aside rounds for inspection or prefer to run 50 rounds with extra space for powder dispensing these trays have you covered. products.name: L.E. Wilson Case Trimmer Platform
products.description:
The Wilson Case Trimmer Platform is a versatile and essential accessory for precision reloaders. Designed to complement the L.E. Wilson trimmer series this platform provides a stable and organized workspace for your case trimming needs.

Works with Wilson Regular and 50 Caliber Trimmer Stands.

Key Features:

  • Efficient Storage: The platform includes dedicated storage space for up to nine (9) case holders ensuring your tools are always within reach.
  • Integrated Tapping Block: A built-in tapping block allows easy removal of cases from the holder streamlining your reloading process.
  • Durable Construction: Made from high-quality polyethylene the platform is sturdy and lightweight offering long-lasting performance.
  • Secure Mounting: Equipped with rubber feet for stability the platform can also be c-clamped to your bench for added security during use.

Whether you’re a seasoned reloader or just starting out the L.E. Wilson Trimmer Platform enhances your efficiency and precision making it a must-have addition to your reloading bench.

products.name: Lyman Borecam 2.0 Wireless Bore Camera
products.description: Lyman’s Borecam 2.0 borescope takes barrel inspection to a whole new level! The wireless Borecam 2.0 produces its own WiFi signal which sends super clean and detailed images directly to your phone. No wires or monitors to get in the way during use. Carefully inspect your bores for wear throat erosion tool marks and other rifling damage as well as copper or lead fouling. The Borecam 2.0 will fit 22 caliber and larger barrels and is now equipped with a longer 26” rod. In addition to taking photos the Borecam 2.0 now takes sharp clear videos. The Borecam 2.0’s easy-to-use app makes storing and retrieving photos and video simple. Apps are available for iOS and Android phones and tablets. Borecam includes: Rod with mounted camera 5 interchangeable 90° Mirrors for various calibers and usb cord for charging. NOTE: Unit is rechargeable and is charged by plugging into a usb port on a PC or standard phone charger (not included).

products.name: Lyman X-Block: Gunsmith Bench Block
products.description:
Having the right tool for the job makes any gunsmithing project so much easier! Without the right tool you may damage fine finishes or break parts. The X-Block is the right tool for anyone driving pins out of firearms. It has all the features to get the job done smoothly and professionally. The X-Block has both a “V” slot and a rounded slot running across the face of the block to support a variety of barrels and slides. The block is made of a tough non-marring polymer. The block has multiple holes to take on most any project as well as a molded in magnet on the back side of the block to catch pins and other small parts as they drop out. Its large 5” diameter provides a stable base with plenty of support.
•    Large 5” diameter
•    Magnet molded into base to catch pins or small parts
•    Made of tough non-marring polymer
•    “V” slot and rounded slot run across the block face to fit most every need such as pistol barrels slides and frames

products.name: Lyman Turbo Super Sifter
products.description:
The LymanTurbo Super Sifter allows cases to easily be separated from media while positioned over 7 5 3 or 2 gallon pails. These commonly available pails make the perfect container for storing used media. The sifter is equipped with large handles to make it easy to use with large volumes of cases and media. The extra deep design prevents media from spilling over the edges when pouring case and media from the tumbler and when in use.

  • Works with commonly available 7 5 3 and 2 gallon pails
  • Extra deep design keeps media inside the sifter and off the floor
  • Large handles make the sifter easy to use

products.name: Lyman Turbo Charger Media Reactivator
products.description:
Lyman Turbo Charger Media Reactivator is a quick and easy way to restore your used corncob media back to its original polishing performance. Not only is this media reactivator easy to use but it is affordable and highly effective. Simply follow the instructions and add the reactivator directly to the used media to give it new life.

Rather than constantly buying new containers of corncob tumbler media why not use Lyman Turbo Charger Media Reactivator to give your used media new life? Available in 4-ounce and 16-ounce bottles this media reactivator is a must-have for serious reloaders.

products.name: Lyman Stainless Steel Pin Magnet
products.description: Lyman's stainless steel pin transfer magnet is the answer for separating our cases from the media pings used in rotary tumblers. Simply pass the magnet over the mixture of case and pins and the pins will be pulled out and grabbed by the magnet. To release the pins just pull up on the handle. The large diameter strong magnet will collect many pins in a single pass. Fast convenient and simply to use! A perfect companion for your tumbler.

products.name: Cyclone Case Dryer 115v
products.description: The perfect companion to any Ultrasonic or Rotary cleaning system. No longer will it be necessary to have to wait days for your brass to air dry! The forced heated air circulation of the Cyclone will dry your brass inside and out within an hour or two with no unsightly water spots. The individual trays can keep your different caliber cases separate. Additionally the dryer can also be used for gun parts that have been ultrasonically cleaned.

products.name: Lyman Pro Maximum Cartridge Gauge 9mm Luger
products.description:
Lyman Pro Maximum Cartridge Gauges have more features than any cartridge gauge on the market! Inspired by Lyman Pro Die Sets the gauges are precision machined from corrosion resistant stainless steel for a long rust-free life. The outside flats prevent rolling and the o-rings provide a non-slip grip.

Pro Maximum Cartridge Gauges check pistol ammunition for case length diameter and overall cartridge length. This inspection is considered mandatory by top competitive shooters who demand 100% reliability for their competition ammo.

products.description:

Lyman Pro Headspace Gauges have more features than any headspace gauge on the market. Inspired by the Lyman Pro Die Sets the gauges are precision machined from corrosion resistant stainless steel for a long rust-free life.

The outside flats prevent rolling and the o-rings provide a non-slip grip. Pro Headspace gauges check maximum and minimum cartridge headspace as well as maximum case length. Headspace gauges are recommended when setting up sizing dies for any bottle neck cartridge.

products.name: Lyman Flash Hole Cleaner
products.description:
The Lyman Flash Hole Cleaner is just the tool you need to quickly and easily remove accumulated residue from the flash hole of your cases to ensure uniform ignition and a more consistent primer spark. Not only is this tool easy to use but its compact size makes it easy to carry as well.

If you are looking for a simple but effective tool to remove accumulated residue from the flash hole of your cartridge cases look no further than this Lyman Flash Hole Cleaner. After cleaning your cartridge cases simply use the Lyman Flash Hole Cleaner to clean the flash hole to achieve more uniform ignition.

products.name: Lyman Flash Hole Uniformer
products.description:
The Lyman Flash Hole Uniformer is a great tool to have on hand for removing flash hole burrs. With a steel cutter and an adjustable stop collar you can use this tool for any size cartridge case. Simply insert the tool and give it a single clockwise turn to quickly and easily remove burrs.

If you are looking for a precise flash hole uniformer look no further than the Lyman Flash Hole Uniformer

products.name: Lyman Primer Pocket Reamer- Small
products.description: The Pocket Reamer removes military crimps and rough metal edges from primer pocket. It?s a must for all reloaders. Available in large or small size

products.name: Lyman Primer Pocket Reamer Large
products.description: The Lyman Primer Pocket Reamer is a must-have tool for reloaders who prefer military cases. This handheld tool features a molded plastic handle with rubber grips for a secure and comfortable grip during use

products.name: Lyman VLD (Very Low Drag) Chamfer/Reamer
products.description: Lyman's VLD Chamfer/ Reamer eliminates damage to bullets caused by the sharp edges of the cartridge case neck. The long boat tail on VLD bullets are cut by the case mouth when chamfered with a standard 45 degree reamer. The sharp 22 degrees on the VLD reamer allows all bullets to slip easily into the case ensuring the best accuracy. Recommended for Sierra VLD and Other Mfg's VLD Bullets.

products.name: Lyman Primer Pocket Cleaner - Large
products.description:
The Lyman Primer Pocket Cleaner is just the tool you need to clean your primer pockets to facilitate uniform primer seating. This tool features a molded plastic handle with rubber grips for a secure and comfortable grip during use and comes in both large and small sizes.

If you are looking for an easy-to-use primer pocket cleaning tool for all of your case prep needs look no further than the Lyman Primer Pocket Cleaner. Available in two sizes this primer pocket cleaner helps to remove fouling from the bottom of your primer pockets leaving them clean and as good as new.

products.name: Lyman Primer Pocket Cleaner - Small
products.description:
The Lyman Primer Pocket Cleaner is just the tool you need to clean your primer pockets to facilitate uniform primer seating. This tool features a molded plastic handle with rubber grips for a secure and comfortable grip during use and comes in both large and small sizes.

If you are looking for an easy-to-use primer pocket cleaning tool for all of your case prep needs look no further than the Lyman Primer Pocket Cleaner. Available in two sizes this primer pocket cleaner helps to remove fouling from the bottom of your primer pockets leaving them clean and as good as new.

products.name: Lyman Case Care Kit
products.description: This Lyman Case Care Kit contains everything you need to prep your favorite cases. Included in this kit is the handy Lyman utility crank that includes an adapter

products.name: Lyman Case Prep Multi-Tool
products.description:
This Lyman Case Prep Multi Tool is a double-ended storage tool for all of your favorite case prep accessories. This compact multi tool was designed specifically for reloaders like to you give you an all-in-one storage solution to make sure that you never misplace your case prep tools.

Not only is the Lyman Case Prep Multi Tool compact for easy carry but it features a unique handle that unthreads in the middle allowing you to store your case prep tools inside. As an added bonus both ends are threaded to allow the mounting of two tools at the same time.

products.name: Lyman Case Prep Multi Tool .50 BMG
products.description: This Lyman Case Prep Multi Tool was specifically designed for .50 BMG enthusiasts to store all of your favorite case prep tools. This double-ended multi tool features a unique handle that unthreads in the middle so you can store your case prep tools inside the device.

products.name: Lyman Case Prep Multi Tool .50 BMG
products.description: This Lyman Case Prep Multi Tool was specifically designed for .50 BMG enthusiasts to store all of your favorite case prep tools. This double-ended multi tool features a unique handle that unthreads in the middle so you can store your case prep tools inside the device.

products.name: Lyman Deburring Tool for .17 to .45 cal Cases
products.description: Bevels and removes burrs from both inside and outside of case mouth. Precision machined and hardened fits all cases from .17 to .45 caliber.

products.name: Lyman Universal Case Prep Accessory Tool Set
products.description:
The Lyman Universal Case Prep Accessory Tool Set is the perfect storage solution for keeping all of your favorite case prep tools in one place. This stylish zippered carry case features eight slots to hold all of the most popular case prep tools for easy carry and transportation in the field or to the range.

Included in the Lyman Universal Case Prep Accessory Tool Set are both small and large primer pocket reamers and cleaners as well as an outside deburring tool and an inside Very Low Drag chamfer tool. All of the tools have a molded plastic handle with a rubber insert for a firm and secure grip during use.

products.name: Lyman Primer Pocket Uniformer - Large
products.description: The Lyman Primer Pocket Uniformer is just the tool you need to ensure uniform primer depth in your reloaded cartridge cases for precision accuracy. These tool features a pre-set stop collar that is set to SAAMI specifications

products.name: Lyman Pistol Primer Pocket Uniformer - Large
products.description: This precision tool allows reloaders to produce a uniform primer depth for more consistent ignition and improves accuracy. Uniforming tool has a pre-set stop collar set to SAAMI specs. Reloader simply inserts and turns. Available in large and small sizes. For pistol cases only.

products.name: Lyman Case Prep Center Xpress - 115 volt
products.description:
The Case Prep Express is an all-inclusive System offering all the most popular case prep accessories driven by a high torque gear motor. The Case Prep Xpress allows the user to simultaneously do 5 different case prep operations. Removable dump pan provides easy clean up of brass shavings. The best part is that all accessories are included from the start no need to have to separately purchase expensive additional accessories.

  • Inside Deburr (VLD) Tool
  • Outside Deburr Tool
  • Primer Pocket Uniformers (Small & Large)
  • Primer Pocket Reamers (Small & Large)
  • Primer Pocket Cleaners (Small & Large)
  • Case Neck Brushes (25 Cal 30 Cal 38 Cal 45 Cal)
  • Case Neck Lube (Mica)
  • Removable Brass Shavings Dump pan
  • Clean-up Brush

products.description: Lyman's Outside Chamfer Tool easily deburrs the outside case mouth to leave a smooth even finish. Works on cartridges from 17 cal to 45 cal. Complements the VLD (Very Low Drag) Inside Chamfer Tool.

products.name: Lyman E-ZEE Trimmer Rifle Set 5 Pilots for .223 .243 .270 30-06 & .308
products.description:
Rifle Set includes pilots for .223 .243 .270 30-06 & .308

Precision case trimming by hand or with power attachment.

The industry leader in trimming and case prep innovation Lyman introduces a new case trimming system for the reloader interested in economy or preferring to have an individual precision hand system for each caliber. The E-ZEE TRIM case trimming system allows the user to trim cases by hand or with a power attachment (included) to precise pre-set length - no adjustment of measuring needed. The trimmer comes with a case locking device cutter trim-to-length pilot cutter head and both hand and power trimming adapters. The trimmer works with any standard shellholder including Lyman Redding RCBS Hornady & Lee Precision. Assembles in seconds and you are ready to trim cases. The E-ZEE TRIM system comes in three practical variations.

products.name: Lyman Nine Pilot Multi-Pack
products.description:
The Lyman Nine Pilot Multi-Pack includes all nine of the most popular case trimmer pilots for use with nearly every caliber cartridge. The pilots included in this multi-pack are as follows: #22 #24 #27 #28 #30 9mm #35 #44 and #45A.

With the Lyman Nine Pilot Multi-Pack you can safely and efficiently trim cartridge cases of all calibers including popular models like the .22 Hornet the .222 Remington the .270 Winchester the .30 Luger the .38 Smith & Wesson the .44 Magnum and the .45 Colt.

products.name: Lyman Replacement Cutter Head
products.description:
The Lyman Replacement Cutter Head comes in a convenient two-pack to replace the cutter on your Lyman Universal Trimmer. The Lyman Universal Trimmer is a must-have for serious reloaders because it makes trimming your cartridge cases fast and easy thanks to the fully adjustable cutting blade.

When the blade on your Lyman Universal Trimmer goes dull or breaks you will be glad to have a Lyman Replacement Cutter Head on hand. Simply swap out the old cutter for the new and your Lyman Universal Trimmer will be back up and running in no time.

products.name: Lyman Carbide Cutter Head
products.description: Lyman Carbide Cutter Head is an optional carbide cutter fits all Lyman trimmers. Ideal for high-volume reloading press.

products.name: Lyman Universal Case Trimmer with Pilot
products.description:
Trim virtually all cases from .22 to .458 without additional collets.

Lyman's Universal Trimmer features the patented Universal Chuckhead which handles any case from .17 caliber to .458. No costly collets required! Features coarse and fine adjustments. Adjusting ring lets you "dial in to an approximate setting for quick repeatability". Includes 9 of the most popular pilots. Additional pilots add even greater range of calibers. Optional power adapter lets you upgrade to power in seconds.

products.name: Lyman Universal Trimmer Power Adapter
products.description: Economical power trimming for reloaders who already own Lyman's original Universal Trimmer. Quickly convert to power trimming. Replace the existing trimmer shaft with the power adapter shaft and attach your drill. You're ready to power trim over 250 cases an hour. The adapter shaft comes with its own cutter and stop collars so you can convert back and forth from power to hand operation. The power adapter only fits the Lyman Universal Trimmer.

products.name: Lyman Universal Trimmer Power Pack Combo
products.description:
The Lyman Universal Trimmer Power Pack Combo is the ideal combination of Lyman's Universal Trimmer and a power adapter which quickly and easily converts your hand-operated trimmer into a power trimmer. All you need is a power screwdriver or an electric drill.

Not only does the Lyman Universal Trimmer Power Pack Combo make power trimming easier than ever but it has the capacity to trim more than 250 cases per hour. The adapter shaft includes a super-sharp cutter as well as stop collars so you are able to switch back and forth between hand trimming and power trimming without having to change settings.

products.name: Lyman Universal Carbide Case Trimmer
products.description: The new Universal Carbide Case Trimmer features a premium Carbide Cutter Head with a fine grain and ultra-sharp cutting edge. The new Carbide Head will hold its edge longer making this Trimmer ideal for volume reloaders. The popular patented Universal Chuckhead handles any case from .17 caliber to .458 caliber with no collets required. The Trimmer includes 9 of the most popular pilots.

products.name: Lyman Brass-Smith Case Trim Xpress 115V
products.description:
Lyman's Case Trim Xpress is a game-changer for rifle reloaders seeking efficiency and precision in case trimming. Eliminating the need for power drills or separate motors its built-in power source and robust variable speed motor ensure quick and clean trims directly on your bench. Designed specifically for bottle neck type cases the Case Trim Xpress utilizes bushings that contact the case shoulder offering rapid and clean trims with its durable carbide cutter.

Included with the unit is a set of 10 orange bushings catering to the most popular bottleneck rifle cases. These bushings spring-loaded for smooth operation support and center the case against the cutter without the need for pilots achieving about 15 cases trimmed per minute. The innovative adjustment wheel allows reloaders to precisely dial in case lengths to .001” increments enhancing the accuracy of every reload.

  • Variable Speed and Power: Integrated power source with variable speed for quick clean trims.
  • Precision Cutting: Utilizes a durable carbide cutter for fast and accurate case trimming.
  • Bushing System: Includes 10 bushings for popular bottleneck cartridges no pilots needed.
  • Efficient Operation: Spring-loaded bushings allow trimming of approximately 15 cases per minute.
  • Compact Design: Low profile space-saving housing perfect for any reloading bench setup.

Moreover the Case Trim Xpress is built with endurance in mind tested to withstand a lifetime of use. It's not suitable for straight wall cases focusing instead on providing the best experience for bottleneck cartridges. The device’s compact and low-profile design ensures it occupies minimal space on your reloading bench making it an essential tool for reloaders who value efficiency and precision.

It features it's own power source so there's no need for power drills or separate motors. By utilizing shoulder contact from the bushing the Case Trim Xpress will quickly and easily trim brass and with spring loaded bushings you can average 15 cases per minute! European plug.

products.name: Lyman 50 BMG Accu Trimmer with Pilot
products.description:
The Lyman 50 BMG Accu Trimmer with Pilot is one of the most powerful yet reasonably priced 50 BMG case trimmers on the market. This trimmer was designed specifically with 50 BMG enthusiasts in mind built to ensure that you need only buy one trimmer no adapters or additional accessories required.

This Lyman 50 BMG Accu Trimmer with Pilot is just what you need to perfectly align and trim your 50 BMG cases. Simply slip the shell head into the Special holder to center it perfectly with the cutting shaft to ensure quick and easy trimming. It is as easy as that!

products.name: Lyman AccuTrimmer Incl/ 9 Pilots
products.description:
The Lyman Accu Trimmer is a great example of Lyman quality in an affordably priced package. This trimmer is just the tool you need to trim all kinds of brass cases between .17 and .458 caliber which gives reloaders like you the versatility you need.

Not only does the Lyman Accu Trimmer accommodate brass cases between .17 and .458 caliber but it incorporates the use of standard shellholders to properly position the cartridges as well as standard Lyman cutter pilots and heads. This tool is available with Lyman

products.name: MEC Super Sizer
products.description:
For shotshell reloading the MEC Super Sizer is a favorite choice by novice and seasoned reloaders alike. Included with the sizer is a power ring collet device for perfect sizing. With an eight-finger design made from steel the back of the base can be resized to its original dimension with very little effort.

This particular sizer is also an excellent option for someone interested in updating a more conventional loader and is designed to accept all lengths of shotshell. The frame is made from durable steel and all necessary hardware is included.

  • Re-sizes shells for the most exacting shotguns
  • Updates conventional reloaders with MEC's exclusive Power-Ring collet resizing device
  • Eight steel fingers encircle the base and apply even pressure until the base is reshaped back to its original size
  • Available in 10 12 16 20 28 gauge and .410 bore

products.name: RifleKuhl Barrel Cooler (Internet packaging)
products.description: Tired of waiting and waiting for your rifle to cool down? MagnetoSpeed?s new barrel cooler Riflekhl is designed to get barrel temperatures down to intended operating levels quickly. The turbocharger inspired impeller is engineered to produce great air flow in a small package. Powered by a single CR123A Lithium battery (included) ambient air is forced through the extendable nozzle down the bore of the rifle. Designed to seal and push air flow down the barrel where it?s needed to efficiently cool barrels typically under 7 minutes. Riflekhl doubles as a chamber flag and features an exclusive built-in air filter to prevent dust and dirt from being blown into your rifle. Spend less time waiting and more time shooting with the MagnetoSpeed Riflekhl.

products.name: NcStar MagPopper Magazine Disassembly Tool for Glock Magazines
products.description:
Features:

  • The innovative MagPopper tool will help you disassemble your Glock magazines in seconds.
  • Works with most factory Glock flat floorplates. Works with 10 round standard capacity and high capacity Glock magazines.
  • Simply insert the hook from the small lever into the floor plate rest the MagPopper body against the front of the magazine body. With one hand grasp the MagPopper and the magazine body and gently squeze. The floor plate will slide forward and unlock from the side magazine tabs with very little effort.
  • Caution magazines are under spring tension. After you have unlocked the floor plate carefully slide/remove the floor plate locking plate spring and follower from the magazine body for service/cleaning.
  • MagPopper also features: a bottle opener a hole on the main body for mounting onto key rings and a " hex hole for holding " screwdriver bits.
  • Compact design for convenient storage.
  • Steel construction.

products.name: NcStar VISM Universal Rear Sight Tool
products.description:
Features:

  • Universal Pistol Rear Sight Tool designed for: Removal Installation and Adjusting windage of dovetailed rear sights for most Semi-Auto Pistol slides.
  • The Universal Pistol Rear Sight Tool works with many types of semi-auto slides: full compact sub compact and pocket sized semi-auto pistols.
  • Base platform is adjustable for height to get your slide and rear sights at the proper height for the rear sight pusher. Includes one bottom spacer for some pocket pistol slides for proper height alignment.
  • Multiple Vertical and Horizontal clamps to secure various sizes and types of semi-auto slides in the tool.
  • Adjustable top brace with plastic insert to secure the slide?s vertical placement on the base platform.
  • Adjustable side braces with plastic inserts to secure the slides horizontal placement on the base platform. Includes two sets of side plastic inserts: a pair of flat inserts and a pair of stepped inserts to fit a wide variety of slide profiles.
  • Rear sight pusher will work with 90 degree and 30 degree rear sight profiles. Rear sight pusher can remove install or adjust the rear sights in either direction.
  • Side witness windows machined into both sides of tool frame to check for and verify proper tool and rear sight alignment.
  • Sight tool frame can be bolted to clamped onto work surface or clamped onto a work vice.
  • Rear sight pusher tool has an adjustable/removable handle or you can use a 15mm wrench or socket tool.
  • Heavy duty Blue Anodized aluminum frame with steel tools
  • Sight pusher steel screw has brass bushings for good bearing surface characteristics and excellent strength.
  • Carrying bag included.
  • US. PAT. 9784535
  • US. PAT. D829294
